#. [message], speaker=Marogin
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\06_Zei.cfg:2350
msgid ""
"If you go north, know that only orcs come back from this direction since "
"last night's attack. If you wipe out the scum prowling around Qyizu's pass, "
"it will be far easier for us to make the road safe when the captain will "
"order us."
msgstr ""
"Si vas al norte, sabe que solo orcos regresan de esta dirección desde el "
"ataque de anoche. Si eliminas la escoria merodeando alrededor del paso de "
"Qyizu, será mucho más fácil para nosotros hacer el camino seguro cuando el "
"capitán nos ordene."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\06_Zei.cfg:2385
msgid ""
"I think we are done with Zei. I would rather go back to the Arable "
"Highlands, but the kingdom needs us."
msgstr ""
"Creo que terminamos con Zei. Preferiría volver a las Tierras Altas Arables, "
"pero el reino nos necesita."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\06_Zei.cfg:2401
msgid "We don't have enough food to continue our journey."
msgstr "No tenemos suficiente comida para continuar nuestro viaje."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\06_Zei.cfg:2418
msgid "We don't have anything to transport our food."
msgstr "No tenemos nada para transportar nuestra comida."

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\06_Zei.cfg:2444
msgid "The inhabitants should be able to fish now."
msgstr "Los habitantes deberían poder pescar ahora."

#. [scenario], id=07_Yooradweak_s_pass
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:4
msgid "Yooradweak's pass"
msgstr "Paso de Yooradweak"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:41
msgid "Get to the other side of Yooradweak's pass"
msgstr "Llega al otro lado del paso de Yooradweak"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:57
msgid "Clear Yooradweak's pass"
msgstr "Despeja el paso de Yooradweak"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:73
msgid "Find another way to Udxatfe"
msgstr "Encuentra otra forma de llegar a Udxatfe"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:95
msgid "Find the entrance of Uvju's cross"
msgstr "Encuentra la entrada de la cruz de Uvju"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:124
msgid "Free the northern watchtower before completing the main objective"
msgstr ""
"Libera la torre de vigilancia norte antes de completar el objetivo principal"

#. [message], speaker=Csia
#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:359
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:373
msgid ""
"Our next stop is Udxatfe. We need to tell the guardian about what happened "
"here in Zei."
msgstr ""
"Nuestra próxima parada es Udxatfe. Necesitamos decirle al guardián sobre lo "
"que pasó aquí en Zei."

#. [message], speaker=Csia
#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:363
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:377
msgid ""
"He will surely be able to draw more information with his knowledge than we "
"with ours."
msgstr ""
"Seguramente podrá obtener más información con su conocimiento que nosotros "
"con el nuestro."

#. [message], speaker=Csia
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:367
msgid ""
"The shortest way is to go west through Yooradweak's pass then through "
"Qyizu's mines"
msgstr ""
"El camino más corto es ir al oeste a través del paso de Yooradweak y luego a "
"través de las minas de Qyizu"

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:381
msgid ""
"From what I know, the shortest way is to go west through Yooradweak's pass."
msgstr ""
"Por lo que sé, el camino más corto es ir al oeste a través del paso de "
"Yooradweak."

#. [message], speaker=Csia
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:394
msgid ""
"We must expect to encounter orcish resistance there. Clearing the pass will "
"benefit us but also the people of Zei."
msgstr ""
"Debemos esperar encontrar resistencia orca allí. Despejar el paso nos "
"beneficiará pero también a la gente de Zei."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:411
msgid "Uvju's cross"
msgstr "Cruz de Uvju"

#. [message], speaker=Csia
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:429
msgid ""
"The pass is on the other side of the bridge. The tower you see south is "
"Zei's northern watchtower."
msgstr ""
"El paso está al otro lado del puente. La torre que ves al sur es la torre de "
"vigilancia norte de Zei."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:446
msgid ""
"North: Uvju's cross\n"
"West: Zei\n"
"East: Qyizu, Udxatfe"
msgstr ""
"Norte: Cruz de Uvju\n"
"Oeste: Zei\n"
"Este: Qyizu, Udxatfe"

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:477
msgid "I think we found the northern watchtower."
msgstr "Creo que encontramos la torre de vigilancia norte."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:483
msgid "A lot of men have died here."
msgstr "Muchos hombres murieron aquí."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:487
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:828
msgid "There is a lever on the floor."
msgstr "Hay una palanca en el suelo."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:497
msgid ""
"It might be the way to open the arsenal. I hope the orcs haven't found it "
"first."
msgstr ""
"Podría ser la forma de abrir el arsenal. Espero que los orcos no lo hayan "
"encontrado antes."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:503
msgid "Should I pull it?"
msgstr "¿Debería tirar de ella?"

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:570
msgid "The arsenal is opened. Alas it looks like the orcs are already in."
msgstr "El arsenal está abierto. Lástima, parece que los orcos ya entraron."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:576
msgid "It opened a secret passage."
msgstr "Abrió un pasaje secreto."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:600
msgid "The doors are closed. Let's try to open them."
msgstr "Las puertas están cerradas. Intentemos abrirlas."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:619
msgid ""
"I can't open it. It looks like someone has stacked rocks on the other side "
"of the door."
msgstr ""
"No puedo abrirla. Parece que alguien ha apilado rocas al otro lado de la "
"puerta."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:623
msgid "I don't know if orcs or humans did it, but we can't use the pass."
msgstr "No sé si orcos o humanos lo hicieron, pero no podemos usar el paso."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:627
msgid "We need to find another way to reach Udxatfe."
msgstr "Necesitamos encontrar otra forma de llegar a Udxatfe."

#. [message], speaker=Csia
#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:637
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:660
msgid "There is a way."
msgstr "Hay una forma."

#. [message], speaker=Csia
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:641
msgid ""
"A tunnel run through the mountain. It begins in Uvju's cross and end on the "
"other side of the pass."
msgstr ""
"Un túnel atraviesa la montaña. Comienza en la cruz de Uvju y termina al otro "
"lado del paso."

#. [message], speaker=Csia
#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:645
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:668
msgid "But this is a dark way, full of horrors from the War of Legions."
msgstr ""
"Pero este es un camino oscuro, lleno de horrores de la Guerra de Legiones."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:649
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:672
msgid "We don't have much choice. We must carry the message to Udxatfe."
msgstr "No tenemos mucha opción. Debemos llevar el mensaje a Udxatfe."

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:664
msgid ""
"I've read that a tunnel run through the mountain. It begins in Uvju's cross "
"and end on the other side of the pass."
msgstr ""
"He leído que un túnel atraviesa la montaña. Comienza en la cruz de Uvju y "
"termina al otro lado del paso."

#. [message], speaker=Ofcuu
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:692
msgid "I’m glad to see another human."
msgstr "Me alegra ver a otro humano."

#. [message], speaker=Csia
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:702
msgid "Who are you, soldier?"
msgstr "¿Quién eres, soldado?"

#. [message], speaker=Ofcuu
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:714
msgid ""
"My troops and I tried to flee from the orcs when they invaded Qyizu, but "
"Zei’s road being blocked, our only option was to go through Uvju’s cross."
msgstr ""
"Mis tropas y yo intentamos huir de los orcos cuando invadieron Qyizu, pero "
"el camino de Zei estando bloqueado, nuestra única opción era ir a través de "
"la cruz de Uvju."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:718
msgid "This is not..."
msgstr "Esto no es..."

#. [message], speaker=Ofcuu
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:722
msgid ""
"What a monumental mistake we made there. We had made half the way when those "
"eight-legged monsters began coming in bulk out of the tunnels."
msgstr ""
"Qué error monumental cometimos allí. Habíamos hecho la mitad del camino "
"cuando esos monstruos de ocho patas comenzaron a salir en masa de los "
"túneles."

#. [message], speaker=Ofcuu
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:726
msgid "We took to our heels, but… "
msgstr "Huimos, pero… "

#. [message], speaker=Ofcuu
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:730
msgid "But… "
msgstr "Pero… "

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:734
msgid "But what?"
msgstr "¿Pero qué?"

#. [message], speaker=Ofcuu
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:738
msgid "My God! How deafening were their screams."
msgstr "¡Dios mío! ¡Qué ensordecedores eran sus gritos."

#. [message], speaker=Ofcuu
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:742
msgid "Why does this happen to me? Why?"
msgstr "¿Por qué me pasa esto a mí? ¿Por qué?"

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:746
msgid ""
"I don't think we will get more info from him. What happened in there seems "
"to have broken his mind."
msgstr ""
"No creo que obtengamos más información de él. Lo que pasó allí parece haber "
"roto su mente."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:769
msgid "I think I found Aldrsil's axe."
msgstr "Creo que encontré el hacha de Aldrsil."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:805
msgid ""
"If we had any other choice, I would rather us not have to pass through "
"Uvju's cross, especially after what Ofcuu told us."
msgstr ""
"Si tuviéramos otra opción, preferiría no tener que pasar por la cruz de "
"Uvju, especialmente después de lo que nos dijo Ofcuu."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:809
msgid ""
"Unfortunately, the pass is blocked, and we have to warn the guardian of "
"Udxatfe."
msgstr ""
"Desafortunadamente, el paso está bloqueado, y tenemos que advertir al "
"guardián de Udxatfe."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:813
msgid "Let's enter the tunnels but be careful everyone."
msgstr "Entremos a los túneles pero sean cuidadosos todos."

#. [message], speaker=Raffolk
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:832
msgid "Hello there. Do you intend to go inside Uvju's cross?"
msgstr "Hola. ¿Piensan entrar en la cruz de Uvju?"

#. [message], speaker=Io
#. [1]
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:836
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\19b_Northern_Lights.cfg:435
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\19b_Northern_Lights.cfg:449
msgid "Yes?"
msgstr "¿Sí?"

#. [message], speaker=Raffolk
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:840
msgid ""
"At this time of year, at this time of day, in this part of the country, "
"without a healer?"
msgstr ""
"¿En esta época del año, a esta hora del día, en esta parte del país… sin un "
"sanador?"

#. [message], speaker=Io
#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:844 .\utils\help.cfg:19
msgid "Yes."
msgstr "Sí."

#. [message], speaker=Raffolk
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:848
msgid "...May I see that?"
msgstr "…¿Puedo verlo?"

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:852
msgid "...No."
msgstr "…No."

#. [message], speaker=Raffolk
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:856
msgid ""
"You know what? I will come anyway.\n"
"Leaving you enter the cross without a healer would be like killing you "
"myself."
msgstr ""
"¿Sabes qué? Voy a ir de todos modos.\n"
"Dejar que entren en la cruz sin un sanador sería como matarlos yo mismo."

#. [message], speaker=Raffolk
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:861
msgid ""
"But take note that I will not fight for you and will leave when we arrive in "
"Qyizu."
msgstr ""
"Pero ten en cuenta que no voy a pelear por ustedes y me iré cuando lleguemos "
"a Qyizu."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:865
msgid "But we did not ask for your help."
msgstr "Pero no te pedimos ayuda."

#. [message], speaker=Raffolk
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:869
msgid "Come on! Let's go!"
msgstr "¡Vamos, en marcha!"

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:923
msgid ""
"There are too many orcs between us and Udxatfe. How are we supposed to get "
"there?"
msgstr ""
"Hay demasiados orcos entre nosotros y Udxatfe. ¿Cómo se supone que lleguemos "
"allí?"

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:941
msgid ""
"The pass is blocked. There is no way we will be able to reach Udxatfe and "
"warn the guardian."
msgstr ""
"El paso está bloqueado. No hay forma de que podamos llegar a Udxatfe y "
"advertir al guardián."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:959
msgid ""
"If trained men weren't able to go through Uvju's cross, how could we? We are "
"barely able to kill some orcs."
msgstr ""
"Si hombres entrenados no pudieron pasar por la cruz de Uvju, ¿cómo "
"podríamos? Somos apenas capaces de matar algunos orcos."

#. [scenario], id=08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:4
msgid "Inside Uvju's cross"
msgstr "Dentro de la cruz de Uvju"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:38
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\09_Spider_Maze.cfg:31
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:41
msgid "Find the exit of Uvju's cross"
msgstr "Encuentra la salida de la cruz de Uvju"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:43
msgid "Defeat the enemy leader before exiting"
msgstr "Derrota al líder enemigo antes de salir"

#. [side], type=Monstrosity LotI
#. [side], type=Skeleton Archer
#. [side], type=Ghast
#. [side], type=Draug
#. [side], type=Ancient Lich
#. [side], type=Deathlord LotI
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:98
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\09_Spider_Maze.cfg:80
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:89
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\31_Corrupted_Temple.cfg:1233
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\36_Old_Temple_Road.cfg:334
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\37_Old_Temple.cfg:80
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\38_Isut.cfg:110
msgid "Undead"
msgstr "No-muertos"

#. [side], type=Spiderling LoI
#. [side], type=Young Giant Spider LoI
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:437
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\09_Spider_Maze.cfg:270
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:401
msgid "Spiders"
msgstr "Arañas"

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:643
msgid "So, here is the famous Uvju's cross."
msgstr "Así que, aquí está la famosa cruz de Uvju."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:647
msgid "Well, it doesn't look nice anyway. Even without what Ofcuu told us."
msgstr ""
"Bueno, no parece bonito de todos modos. Incluso sin lo que nos dijo Ofcuu."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:651
msgid ""
"However, it is the only way to reach Qyizu now that Yooradweak's pass is "
"blocked. I hope no one is afraid of spiders because I can already hear them."
msgstr ""
"Sin embargo, es la única forma de llegar a Qyizu ahora que el paso de "
"Yooradweak está bloqueado. Espero que nadie tenga miedo a las arañas porque "
"ya las puedo oír."

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:664
msgid ""
"This must be the spiders the demons left. It's impressive that they are "
"still here."
msgstr ""
"Estas deben ser las arañas que dejaron los demonios. Es impresionante que "
"aún estén aquí."

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:668
msgid "But not really reassuring."
msgstr "Pero no realmente tranquilizador."

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:735
msgid "Yes, let's quit this corridor."
msgstr "Sí, salgamos de este corredor."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:862
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:968
msgid "There are spiders coming out of the pits!"
msgstr "¡Hay arañas saliendo de los pozos!"

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:891
msgid "I would love to study them were they not trying to kill us."
msgstr "Me encantaría estudiarlas si no intentaran matarnos."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:912
msgid "There are spiders coming out of the pits and traps!"
msgstr "¡Hay arañas saliendo de los pozos y trampas!"

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:1103
msgid "The books on the shelf are badly damaged."
msgstr "Los libros en el estante están muy dañados."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:1107
msgid "Wait! I found one that should be readable!"
msgstr "¡Espera! ¡Encontré uno que debería ser legible!"

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:1126
msgid "Awesome! Give it to me!"
msgstr "¡Genial! ¡Dámelo!"

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:1148
msgid "The are more mold than paper on this shelf."
msgstr "Hay más moho que papel en este estante."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:1152
msgid ""
"It looks like one of the books has not been completely eaten by the mold."
msgstr ""
"Parece que uno de los libros no ha sido completamente comido por el moho."

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:1171
msgid "Don't touch it! Let me treat it with the care it deserves."
msgstr "¡No lo toques! Déjame tratarlo con el cuidado que merece."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:1190
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\09_Spider_Maze.cfg:565
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:482
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:532
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:665
msgid "There are spiders coming out of the traps!"
msgstr "¡Hay arañas saliendo de las trampas!"

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:1267
msgid "A frightening lot of spiders!"
msgstr "¡Un montón aterrador de arañas!"

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:1333
msgid "Damned orcs! It looks like they have raised undead here too."
msgstr "¡Malditos orcos! Parece que han levantado no-muertos aquí también."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:1337
msgid ""
"If we can find the undead leader and defeat it, it will be easier to exit."
msgstr ""
"Si podemos encontrar al líder no-muerto y derrotarlo, será más fácil salir."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:1361
msgid "Come over here! I think I found something."
msgstr "¡Ven aquí! Creo que encontré algo."

#. [message]
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:1381
msgid "It looks like an elevator. We could use it to go back to the surface."
msgstr "Parece un elevador. Podríamos usarlo para volver a la superficie."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:1391
msgid "Except that I can't see any light when I look up."
msgstr "Excepto que no veo ninguna luz cuando miro arriba."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:1397
msgid "I don't think so... I can't see any light when I look up."
msgstr "No lo creo... No veo ninguna luz cuando miro arriba."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:1403
msgid "I don't see any other path. We must take it and see where it leads to."
msgstr "No veo otro camino. Debemos tomarlo y ver a dónde lleva."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:1425
msgid "Let's go down. I hope the exit is down there and spiders are not."
msgstr "Bajemos. Espero que la salida esté abajo y las arañas no."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:1453
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\09_Spider_Maze.cfg:843
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:1050
msgid "Wait for us! We are still fighting the spiders here!"
msgstr "¡Espérennos! ¡Aún estamos luchando contra las arañas aquí!"

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:1470
msgid "This was one ugly undead. I am quite sure it was leading the others."
msgstr ""
"Este no-muerto era bien feo. Estoy bastante seguro de que era el que los "
"dirigía."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:1474
msgid "It should be easier for us now that it is dead."
msgstr "Debería ser más fácil ahora que está muerto."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:1482
msgid "My God! The screams! They are deafening!"
msgstr "¡Dios mío! ¡Los gritos! ¡Son ensordecedores!"

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:1486
msgid "Why is this happening to us? Why?"
msgstr "¿Por qué nos pasa esto? ¿Por qué?"

#. [scenario], id=09_Spider_Maze
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\09_Spider_Maze.cfg:4
msgid "Spider Maze"
msgstr "Laberinto de Arañas"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\09_Spider_Maze.cfg:36
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:46
msgid "Kill all spiders"
msgstr "Mata a todas las arañas"

#. [message]
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\09_Spider_Maze.cfg:523
msgid ""
"I'm afraid we will have to deal with spiders down here too. Probably undead "
"also."
msgstr ""
"Temo que tendremos que lidiar con arañas aquí abajo también. Probablemente "
"no-muertos también."

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\09_Spider_Maze.cfg:536
msgid ""
"It would be a good thing if we were able to get rid of the spiders. That "
"would allow scholars to study that ruin."
msgstr ""
"Sería algo bueno si pudiéramos deshacernos de las arañas. Eso permitiría a "
"los eruditos estudiar esa ruina."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\09_Spider_Maze.cfg:542
msgid ""
"It would be a good thing if we were able to get rid of the spiders. Not that "
"it would become a popular place, but still."
msgstr ""
"Sería algo bueno si pudiéramos deshacernos de las arañas. No es que se "
"convierta en un lugar popular, pero aun así."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\09_Spider_Maze.cfg:548
msgid ""
"Unfortunately, I'm not sure we have the time to do this. Our main mission "
"remains to warn the guardian."
msgstr ""
"Desafortunadamente, no estoy seguro de que tengamos el tiempo para hacer "
"esto. Nuestra misión principal sigue siendo advertir al guardián."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\09_Spider_Maze.cfg:687
msgid "There is a large rusty door. Should I try to open it?"
msgstr "Hay una puerta grande oxidada. ¿Debería intentar abrirla?"

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\09_Spider_Maze.cfg:689
msgid "Yes, let's fight what's behind."
msgstr "Sí, vamos a enfrentar lo que haya detrás."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\09_Spider_Maze.cfg:731
msgid ""
"There is a large iron door. It looks like there is a huge hall on the other "
"side of it."
msgstr ""
"Hay una puerta grande de hierro. Parece que hay un salón enorme al otro lado."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\09_Spider_Maze.cfg:735
msgid ""
"It would be better to close it back once we will have crossed so that no "
"spider tries to attack us from behind. Should I try to open the door now?"
msgstr ""
"Sería mejor volver a cerrarla una vez que hayamos pasado, para que ninguna "
"araña nos ataque por la espalda. ¿Abro la puerta ahora?"

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\09_Spider_Maze.cfg:778
msgid "There is a large wooden door. Should I open it"
msgstr "Hay una puerta grande de madera. ¿La abro?"

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\09_Spider_Maze.cfg:797
msgid "Caution! A spider was hiding on the ceiling."
msgstr "¡Cuidado! ¡Había una araña escondida en el techo!"

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\09_Spider_Maze.cfg:831
msgid ""
"We have not killed all the spiders before us, but the mission is more "
"important. Let's proceed to this new room."
msgstr ""
"No hemos matado a todas las arañas ante nosotros, pero la misión es más "
"importante. Procedamos a esta nueva habitación."

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\09_Spider_Maze.cfg:868
msgid "I think we killed all the spiders living in this part of Uvju's cross."
msgstr ""
"Creo que matamos a todas las arañas viviendo en esta parte de la cruz de "
"Uvju."

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\09_Spider_Maze.cfg:872
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:1079
msgid "It looks like this one was guarding a treasure."
msgstr "Parece que este estaba cuidando un tesoro."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\09_Spider_Maze.cfg:876
msgid ""
"Let's take it, we will need it for our journey. \n"
"Now, let's proceed to the next room."
msgstr ""
"Tomémoslo, lo necesitaremos para nuestro viaje. \n"
"Ahora, procedamos a la siguiente habitación."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\09_Spider_Maze.cfg:912
msgid "This place is a maze!"
msgstr "¡Este lugar es un laberinto!"

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\09_Spider_Maze.cfg:916
msgid ""
"We spend too much time in there. And we don't even know for sure the exit "
"still exists."
msgstr ""
"Pasamos demasiado tiempo aquí. Y ni siquiera sabemos con seguridad si la "
"salida aún existe."

#. [scenario], id=10_Great_Hall
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:4
msgid "Great Hall"
msgstr "Gran Salón"

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:454
msgid "Wahoo! This room is huge! I'm pretty sure it must be nice to visit."
msgstr ""
"¡Wahoo! ¡Esta habitación es enorme! Estoy seguro de que debe ser bonito "
"visitarla."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:461
msgid "Or at least it would be if it wasn't full of spiders and undead."
msgstr "O al menos lo sería si no estuviera llena de arañas y no-muertos."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:465
msgid "Let's find a way out. I'm getting really tired of all those spiders."
msgstr "Busquemos una salida. Me estoy cansando mucho de todas esas arañas."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:582
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:628
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:785
msgid "Some spiders are born from this sack."
msgstr "Algunas arañas nacen de este saco."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:766
msgid "A lot of spiders!"
msgstr "¡Muchas arañas!"

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:863
msgid "It has closed the door."
msgstr "Cerró la puerta."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:881
msgid "The door is open again."
msgstr "La puerta está abierta otra vez."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:958
msgid ""
"I think I found another elevator! Let's see if this one goes back to the "
"surface."
msgstr ""
"¡Creo que encontré otro elevador! Veamos si este va de vuelta a la "
"superficie."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:962
msgid "I can see the, sun up there. Hurrah!"
msgstr "¡Puedo ver el sol allá arriba. ¡Hurra!"

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:983
msgid ""
"This looks like a bigger version of the spiders. It must be their queen or "
"something like that."
msgstr ""
"Esto parece una versión más grande de las arañas. Debe ser su reina o algo "
"así."

#. [message]
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:987
msgid ""
"I doubt that. Adult Giant Spiders are bigger than that. This must still be a "
"young one."
msgstr ""
"Lo dudo. Las arañas gigantes adultas son mucho más grandes. Esta todavía "
"debe ser joven."

#. [message]
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:991
msgid ""
"It might be commanding the ones that are attacking us, but there must be a "
"mother somewhere."
msgstr ""
"Podría estar dirigiendo a las que nos atacan, pero tiene que haber una madre "
"en alguna parte."

#. [message]
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:1012
msgid "Ah! There it is!"
msgstr "¡Ah! ¡Ahí está!"

#. [message]
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:1016
msgid "This must be the mother. And it seems to be blocking the way."
msgstr "Esta debe ser la madre. Y parece que está bloqueando el camino."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:1038
msgid ""
"Let's go back up. We should arrive on the other side of Yooradweak's pass."
msgstr ""
"Subamos de nuevo. Deberíamos llegar al otro lado del paso de Yooradweak."

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:1075
msgid ""
"I think we killed all the remaining spiders of Uvju's cross. It should be "
"easier to cross for others now."
msgstr ""
"Creo que matamos a todas las arañas restantes de la cruz de Uvju. Debería "
"ser más fácil cruzarla para otros ahora."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:1083
msgid "Let's take it, we will need it for our journey."
msgstr "Tomémoslo, lo necesitaremos para nuestro viaje."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:1109
msgid "Are we going to see an infinite number of spiders?"
msgstr "¿Vamos a ver un número infinito de arañas?"

#. [message], speaker=Csia
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:1113
msgid ""
"Don't be stupid son. A infinite number of something does not exist. There "
"could be a lot of them though."
msgstr ""
"No seas tonto, hijo. Un número infinito de algo no existe. Aunque sí puede "
"haber muchas."

#. [message], speaker=Csia
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:1117
msgid ""
"The good thing is they do not seem to arrive all at once. We simply need to "
"kill them faster than they arrive and move forward."
msgstr ""
"Lo bueno es que no parecen llegar todas a la vez. Solo tenemos que matarlas "
"más rápido de lo que llegan y avanzar."

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:1121
msgid ""
"There has too be a finite number of spiders, because there is no infinite "
"source of food and those things need to eat."
msgstr ""
"Tiene que haber un número finito de arañas, porque no existe una fuente "
"infinita de comida y esas cosas necesitan comer."

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:1125
msgid ""
"There is probably a spider queen somewhere in there that is sending them at "
"us. If we manage to kill it, they should stop coming for us."
msgstr ""
"Probablemente hay una reina araña en algún lugar que las está enviando "
"contra nosotros. Si logramos matarla, deberían dejar de venir."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:1133
msgid "Too many spiders. Too many undead."
msgstr "Demasiadas arañas. Demasiados no-muertos."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:1137
msgid "This place is too huge. The exit could be anywhere."
msgstr ""
"Este lugar es demasiado enorme. La salida podría estar en cualquier lugar."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:1141
msgid "We won't get out of here alive."
msgstr "No saldremos de aquí vivos."

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:1157
msgid "That's it. No more spiders should attack us."
msgstr "Listo. Ya no deberían atacarnos más arañas."

#. [message]
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:1161
msgid "Well yes, but actually no."
msgstr "Bueno, sí… pero en realidad no."

#. [message]
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:1165
msgid ""
"It only means that spiders won't come looking for us anymore. But if we "
"disturb spiders that are there, they will attack us anyway."
msgstr ""
"Solo significa que las arañas ya no vendrán a buscarnos. Pero si molestamos "
"a las que ya están ahí, igual nos atacarán."

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:49
msgid "Save at least one dwarf"
msgstr "Salva al menos un enano"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:59
msgid "Talk to Amin"
msgstr "Habla con Amin"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:77
msgid "Talk to a dwarf"
msgstr "Habla con un enano"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:95
msgid "Enter the mine"
msgstr "Entra a la mina"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:110
msgid "Open the door of Yooradweak's pass"
msgstr "Abre la puerta del paso de Yooradweak"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:110
msgid "(100 gold)"
msgstr "(100 oro)"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:121
msgid "Every dwarf dies"
msgstr "Todos los enanos mueren"

#. [side], type=Dwarvish Fighter
#. [side]
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:354
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\15_Ups_and_Downs.cfg:280
msgid "Dwarves"
msgstr "Enanos"

#. [side], type=Sergeant
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:429
msgid "Zei guards"
msgstr "Guardias de Zei"

#. [side], type=Peasant
#. [side], type=Trapper
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:445
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\23_Abxoowbus_Trading_Post.cfg:330
msgid "Merchants"
msgstr "Mercaderes"

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:472
msgid ""
"Well, it looks like the secret entrance is in a house on the other side."
msgstr "Bueno, parece que la entrada secreta está en una casa al otro lado."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:476
msgid "And outside more orcs."
msgstr "Y afuera más orcos."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:480
msgid "What a surprise."
msgstr "Qué sorpresa."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:488
msgid ""
"Wait! It looks like a few dwarves are getting attacked by the orcs! We need "
"to save them!"
msgstr ""
"¡Espera! ¡Parece que unos pocos enanos están siendo atacados por los orcos! "
"¡Necesitamos salvarlos!"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:529
msgid ""
"East: Zei\n"
"South: Qyizu, Udxatfe\n"
"North-west: Uvju’s Cross, western tower"
msgstr ""
"Este: Zei\n"
"Sur: Qyizu, Udxatfe\n"
"Noroeste: Cruz de Uvju, torre oeste"

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:554
msgid ""
"It looks like the door is blocked by rocks. There's a barrel full of powder "
"next to them. Should I light it up?"
msgstr ""
"Parece que la puerta está bloqueada por rocas. Hay un barril lleno de polvo "
"junto a ellas. ¿Debo encenderlo?"

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:556
msgid "Yes but be careful not to get hurt."
msgstr "Sí, pero cuidado de no salir herido."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:576
msgid ""
"The blast was more powerful than I expected. I don't think it is possible to "
"light those barrels up without being hurt by the explosion."
msgstr ""
"La explosión fue más fuerte de lo que esperaba. No creo que sea posible "
"encender esos barriles sin salir herido por la explosión."

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:582
msgid "No, it's too dangerous."
msgstr "No, es demasiado peligroso."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:601
msgid "The door is now cleared. Should I open it?"
msgstr "La puerta ahora está despejada. ¿Debo abrirla?"

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:603
msgid "Yes, let's open the pass back."
msgstr "Sí, abramos el paso otra vez."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:612
msgid "The door is open."
msgstr "La puerta está abierta."

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:618
msgid "No, wait a bit."
msgstr "No, espera un poco."

#. [message], speaker=Aeraent
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:637
msgid "Well, we were trying to find a way to open this door."
msgstr "Bueno, intentábamos encontrar una forma de abrir esta puerta."

#. [message], speaker=Aeraent
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:641
msgid ""
"You must be the reckless farmer my guards talk to me about. I wouldn’t ’ve "
"believed it if I hadn’t seen it with my own eyes."
msgstr ""
"Debes ser el granjero imprudente del que me hablan mis guardias. No lo "
"habría creído si no lo hubiera visto con mis propios ojos."

#. [message], speaker=Aeraent
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:645
msgid "Tell me, have you really killed all these orcs?"
msgstr "Dime, ¿realmente mataste a todos estos orcos?"

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:649
msgid "Yes, we did."
msgstr "Sí, lo logramos."

#. [message], speaker=Aeraent
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:653
msgid ""
"Zei is hugely indebted to you, pal. We will do our best to keep the lands "
"you’ve conquered for us."
msgstr ""
"Zei está enormemente en deuda contigo, amigo. Haremos lo mejor para mantener "
"las tierras que has conquistado para nosotros."

#. [message], speaker=Aeraent
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:664
msgid "Here is a little reward for having opened the door."
msgstr "Aquí tienes una pequeña recompensa por haber abierto la puerta."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:668
msgid "Thank you, sir."
msgstr "Gracias, señor."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:688
msgid ""
"West: Qyizu's mines, Udxatfe\n"
"South-east: Zei"
msgstr ""
"Oeste: Minas de Qyizu, Udxatfe\n"
"Sureste: Zei"

#. [message], speaker=Giles
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:712
msgid ""
"Wuz crackalackin'. If you wanna git all up in Zei, itz pointless. I heard "
"tha city was burnt some nights ago."
msgstr ""
"¿Qué pasa? Si quieres entrar a Zei, es inútil. Escuché que la ciudad fue "
"quemada hace algunas noches."

#. [message], speaker=Giles
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:717
msgid ""
"We is thinin bout tha way we is goin ta feed our mulez until tha arrival of "
"our associates. "
msgstr ""
"Estamos pensando en la forma de alimentar a nuestras mulas hasta la llegada "
"de nuestros asociados. "

#. [message], speaker=Giles
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:722
msgid "To drop a rhyme tha real deal, one mule should be enough now, nahmeean?"
msgstr ""
"Para decir la verdad, una mula debería ser suficiente ahora, ¿entiendes?"

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:726
msgid ""
"I have no idea what he just said. I think he is trying to sell us a mule."
msgstr ""
"No tengo idea de qué acaba de decir. Creo que está intentando vendernos una "
"mula."

#. [message], speaker=Giles
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:748
msgid "D-ya want a mule? Fo` 10 gold keep'n it real yo?"
msgstr "¿Quieren una mula? ¿Por 10 de oro, sin cuento?"

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:750
msgid "I'm sorry my brave, but we don't need a mule."
msgstr "Lo siento, valiente, pero no necesitamos una mula."

#. [message], speaker=Giles
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:755
msgid "As yo ass wish."
msgstr "Como quieras, socio."

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:762
msgid ""
"Hello, mah brave. We wizzould indee' be interested 'n a M-to-tha-izzule."
msgstr "Hola, valiente. La verdad es que sí nos interesaría una muuula."

#. [message], speaker=Giles
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:777
msgid ""
"I be S-O-Double-Rizzy, bizzy yizzy dizzy have enizzle monizzle (You do not "
"have enough gold)."
msgstr ""
"Soy S-O-Double-Rizzy, ocupado y mareado no tienes suficiente dinero (No "
"tienes suficiente oro)."

#. [unit], id=Darl'n, type=Bay Horse
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:788
msgid "Darl'n"
msgstr "Darl'n"

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:797
msgid "Hizzere is. What her nizzle?"
msgstr "Aquí está. ¿Cómo se llama?"

#. [message], speaker=Giles
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:802
msgid "She be Darl'n. I hizzle she will sizzy you."
msgstr "Se llama Darl'n. Creo que les va a gustar."

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:840 .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:983
msgid "It’s a rough job, but we must live. Besides, we’re not the only ones…"
msgstr "Es un trabajo duro, pero debemos vivir. Además, no somos los únicos…"

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:850
msgid "I'm sorry we couldn't save more of you."
msgstr "Lo siento, no pudimos salvar a más de ustedes."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:856 .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:999
msgid "What were those orcs doing here?"
msgstr "¿Qué hacían esos orcos aquí?"

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:860
msgid ""
"They were looking for magical items. And where do you think the magical "
"items the orcs are stealing go? They end up in the pocket of a Commander "
"Isut."
msgstr ""
"Buscaban objetos mágicos. ¿Y dónde crees que van los objetos mágicos que los "
"orcos están robando? Terminan en el bolsillo de un Comandante Isut."

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:864 .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:1007
msgid "May I be turn into a mule if there is no goblin in all this! "
msgstr "¡Que me convierta en una mula si no hay un goblin en todo esto! "

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:868 .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:1011
msgid "You seem to know a lot about what is happening."
msgstr "Parece que sabes mucho sobre lo que está pasando."

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:872
msgid ""
"My brother Hufifa must know more but the orcs locked him up down there. I "
"would need your help to free him if you agree."
msgstr ""
"Mi hermano Hufifa debe saber más pero los orcos lo encerraron allá abajo. "
"Necesitaría tu ayuda para liberarlo si estás de acuerdo."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:876
msgid ""
"I'm sorry, but we need to reach Udxatfe as fast as possible. We don't have "
"the time to enter the mine to look for your brother."
msgstr ""
"Lo siento, pero necesitamos llegar a Udxatfe lo más rápido posible. No "
"tenemos tiempo para entrar a la mina a buscar a tu hermano."

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:881
msgid ""
"Don't worry. The way to Udxatfe is through the lower level of the mine. "
"That's where my brother is locked. I will show you the way."
msgstr ""
"No te preocupes. El camino a Udxatfe es a través del nivel inferior de la "
"mina. Allí es donde está encerrado mi hermano. Te mostraré el camino."

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:883
msgid "Sure, we will help you."
msgstr "Claro, te ayudaremos."

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:898
msgid ""
"Charge! There are some twenty orcs down there to whom we shall teach some "
"manners!"
msgstr ""
"¡A la carga! ¡Hay unos veinte orcos allá abajo a los que les vamos a enseñar "
"modales!"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:902
msgid "You can now recruit dwarvish fighters."
msgstr "Ahora puedes reclutar luchadores enanos."

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:907
msgid "No, it is too dangerous. We'd rather have you to stay here."
msgstr "No, es demasiado peligroso. Preferimos que te quedes aquí."

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:911
msgid "You understand nothing! "
msgstr "¡No entienden nada!"

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:915
msgid "We are at war right now. Against whom or against what, nobody knows!"
msgstr ""
"¡Estamos en guerra ahora mismo! ¡Contra quién o contra qué, nadie lo sabe!"

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:919
msgid ""
"So, if you think you can get out of it all by yourself, go on, don’t "
"hesitate!"
msgstr "Así que si creen que pueden salir de esto solos, adelante, ¡no duden!"

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:993
msgid "I'm sorry when couldn't save more of you."
msgstr "Lo siento, no pudimos salvar a más de ustedes."

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:1003
msgid ""
"They were looking for magical items. And where do you think go the magical "
"items the orcs are stealing? They end in the pocket of a Commander Isut. "
msgstr ""
"Buscaban objetos mágicos. ¿Y dónde crees que van los objetos mágicos que los "
"orcos están robando? Terminan en el bolsillo de un Comandante Isut. "

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:1015
msgid "Hufifa must know more but the orcs locked him up down there."
msgstr "Hufifa debe saber más pero los orcos lo encerraron allá abajo."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:1019
msgid ""
"I'm sorry, but we need to reach Udxatfe as fast as possible. We don't have "
"the time to enter the mine to look for your friend."
msgstr ""
"Lo siento, pero necesitamos llegar a Udxatfe lo más rápido posible. No "
"tenemos tiempo para entrar a la mina a buscar a tu amigo."

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:1023
msgid ""
"Don't worry. The way to Udxatfe is through the lower level of the mine. "
"That's where Hufifa is locked"
msgstr ""
"No te preocupes. El camino a Udxatfe es a través del nivel inferior de la "
"mina. Allí es donde está encerrado Hufifa"

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:1061
msgid "Well, it looks like we must cross the mines to reach Udxatfe."
msgstr "Bueno, parece que tenemos que cruzar las minas para llegar a Udxatfe."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:1065
msgid "We will try to find and save Hufifa on the way."
msgstr "Intentaremos encontrar y salvar a Hufifa en el camino."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:1069
msgid "He might have valuable information about what is happening."
msgstr "Podría tener información valiosa sobre lo que está pasando."

#. [message], speaker=Raffolk
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:1081
msgid "Well, this is where I leave you. See you around."
msgstr "Bueno, aquí me despido. Nos vemos por ahí."

#. [message], speaker=Csia
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:1108
msgid "The events are too serious that you can continue without a leader."
msgstr ""
"Los acontecimientos son demasiado graves como para que sigan sin un líder."

#. [message], speaker=Csia
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:1118
msgid "I need to go back to Zei and find a way to reopen Yooradweak's pass."
msgstr ""
"Debo volver a Zei y encontrar una forma de reabrir el paso de Yooradweak."

#. [message], speaker=Csia
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:1122
msgid "For the sake of all of us, I hope you will find Teumiuxe alive."
msgstr "Por el bien de todos, espero que encuentren a Teumiuxe con vida."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:1146
msgid "You can no longer recruit nor recall Sergeants."
msgstr "Ya no puedes reclutar ni reincorporar Sargentos."

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:1190
msgid "That's it. The dwarves should be safe."
msgstr "Listo. Los enanos deberían estar a salvo."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:1216
msgid ""
"The dwarves are all dead! How can we imagine saving the country if we can't "
"even save a few persons?"
msgstr ""
"¡Los enanos están todos muertos! ¿Cómo podemos imaginar salvar el país si no "
"podemos ni salvar a unas pocas personas?"

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:1247
msgid ""
"The dwarves have suffered enough. We won't accept gold from them. Only food "
"and rest."
msgstr ""
"Los enanos ya han sufrido bastante. No vamos a aceptar oro de ellos. Solo "
"comida y descanso."

#. [message], speaker=trader
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:1261
msgid "My good friend! Our meeting is certainly a sign of fate."
msgstr ""
"¡Mi buen amigo! Nuestro encuentro es ciertamente una señal del destino."

#. [message], speaker=trader
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:1265
msgid ""
"I need some items to bring them to my… hmmm… commercial partners… and you "
"totally look like you have some."
msgstr ""
"Necesito algunos objetos para llevarlos a mis… hmm… socios comerciales… y tú "
"pareces totalmente tener algunos."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:1269
msgid "Well, we collected some items during our journey."
msgstr "Bueno, recolectamos algunas cosas durante el viaje."

#. [message], speaker=trader
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:1273
msgid ""
"Yes, truly, you have what I need. Would you consent selling me some in "
"exchange for a substantial sum?"
msgstr ""
"Sí, verdaderamente, tienes lo que necesito. ¿Consentirías venderme algunos a "
"cambio de una suma sustancial?"

#. [message], speaker=trader
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:1311
msgid "I notably look for magic goods. If you have some, of course."
msgstr "Notablemente busco bienes mágicos. Si tienes algunos, por supuesto."

