#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:8137
msgid "Bringing back the soul"
msgstr "Traer de vuelta el alma"

#. [message], speaker=trader
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\23_Abxoowbus_Trading_Post.cfg:1185
msgid "Stingy tail"
msgstr "Cola tacaña"

#. [message], speaker=trader
#. [object]
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\23_Abxoowbus_Trading_Post.cfg:1186
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:7409
msgid "Animating skeletons"
msgstr "Animando esqueletos"

#. [message], speaker=trader
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\23_Abxoowbus_Trading_Post.cfg:1391
msgid "I won't sell you food for it to get wasted."
msgstr "No te voy a vender comida para que se desperdicie."

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\23_Abxoowbus_Trading_Post.cfg:1436
msgid "I know this cave."
msgstr "Conozco esta cueva."

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\23_Abxoowbus_Trading_Post.cfg:1440
msgid ""
"It is full of trolls and saurians. They will not be very happy to see us on "
"their territory. "
msgstr ""
"Está llena de trolls y saurios. No van a estar muy contentos de vernos en su "
"territorio."

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\23_Abxoowbus_Trading_Post.cfg:1444
msgid ""
"Unfortunately, this is the shortest way to the eastern swamp, and this is "
"were my staff seems to be."
msgstr ""
"Lamentablemente, es el camino más corto al pantano del este, y parece que mi "
"bastón está ahí."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\23_Abxoowbus_Trading_Post.cfg:1450
msgid ""
"I don't like the look of this cave. I'm sure it is full of deadly creatures, "
"lurking in the dark.  "
msgstr ""
"No me gusta cómo se ve esta cueva. Estoy seguro de que está llena de "
"criaturas mortales acechando en la oscuridad."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\23_Abxoowbus_Trading_Post.cfg:1454
msgid "Unfortunately, it seems to be the only way to continue our travel."
msgstr ""
"Lamentablemente, parece ser el único camino para continuar nuestro viaje."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\23_Abxoowbus_Trading_Post.cfg:1458
msgid "We need to reach the eastern swamp and recover Teumiuxe's staff."
msgstr ""
"Tenemos que llegar al pantano del este y recuperar el bastón de Teumiuxe."

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\24_Deep_Water.cfg:27
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\25_Troll_Cave.cfg:27
msgid "Cross the cave"
msgstr "Cruza la cueva"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\24_Deep_Water.cfg:38
msgid "Stop the agressive fishes before leaving"
msgstr "Detén a los peces agresivos antes de salir"

#. [side], type=Sea Serpent
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\24_Deep_Water.cfg:83
msgid "Fishes"
msgstr "Peces"

#. [side], type=Saurian Ambusher
#. [side], type=Water Serpent
#. [side], type=Saurian Flanker
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\24_Deep_Water.cfg:101
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\25_Troll_Cave.cfg:96
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26_Echo_Chamber.cfg:92
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:75
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:159
msgid "Saurians"
msgstr "Saurios"

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\24_Deep_Water.cfg:357
msgid ""
"I didn't expect so much water in this cave. I can see it streaming down the "
"walls and I can hear droplets falling on the ground."
msgstr ""
"No esperaba tanta agua en esta cueva. Veo cómo corre por las paredes y "
"escucho las gotas cayendo al suelo."

#. [message]
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\24_Deep_Water.cfg:361
msgid "This cave is really special you know."
msgstr "Esta cueva es realmente especial, ¿sabes?"

#. [message]
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\24_Deep_Water.cfg:365
msgid ""
"It was formed a long time ago, when an spell went entropic made an "
"underwater cave rise above the ground."
msgstr ""
"Se formó hace mucho tiempo, cuando un hechizo que se volvió entrópico hizo "
"que una cueva submarina emergiera sobre la superficie."

#. [message]
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\24_Deep_Water.cfg:369
msgid "Since then, the cave still contain water, but also a lot of magic."
msgstr ""
"Desde entonces, la cueva todavía contiene agua, pero también mucha magia."

#. [message]
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\24_Deep_Water.cfg:373
msgid "It is even said that you can meet sea creatures in it."
msgstr "Incluso se dice que se pueden encontrar criaturas marinas aquí dentro."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\24_Deep_Water.cfg:377
msgid "Alright everyone! Try not to slip."
msgstr "¡Muy bien todos! Traten de no resbalar."

#. [message]
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\24_Deep_Water.cfg:381
msgid ""
"The exit should be south. But we will probably have to fight the saurians "
"for that."
msgstr ""
"La salida debería estar al sur. Pero probablemente tendremos que pelear con "
"los saurios para llegar."

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\24_Deep_Water.cfg:400
msgid ""
"I know there is a lot of water here, but I did not expect to see a fish."
msgstr "Sé que hay mucha agua aquí, pero no esperaba ver un pez."

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\24_Deep_Water.cfg:405
msgid ""
"They seem agressive. I am afraid we will have to fight them on top of the "
"saurians."
msgstr ""
"Parecen agresivos. Me temo que tendremos que pelear con ellos además de con "
"los saurios."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\24_Deep_Water.cfg:418
msgid ""
"This horror was probably the mother of the fishes. We should have some peace "
"now."
msgstr ""
"Este horror probablemente era la madre de los peces. Ahora deberíamos tener "
"algo de paz."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\24_Deep_Water.cfg:438
msgid ""
"Crossing this cave is difficult enough with all those saurians, and now we "
"had to fight fishes on top of it."
msgstr ""
"Cruzar esta cueva es lo suficientemente difícil con todos esos saurios, y "
"ahora tuvimos que luchar contra peces además."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\24_Deep_Water.cfg:442
msgid ""
"I don't know how long this cave is, but I hope the situation will be better "
"on the other side of it. "
msgstr ""
"No sé cuán larga es esta cueva, pero espero que la situación sea mejor al "
"otro lado de ella. "

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\24_Deep_Water.cfg:446
msgid "Unfortunately, with what we heard in Udxatfe, I am afraid it won't be."
msgstr "Desafortunadamente, con lo que oímos en Udxatfe, temo que no lo sea."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\24_Deep_Water.cfg:479
msgid "Wait for us! We are still fighting the fishes here!"
msgstr "¡Espérennos! ¡Aún estamos luchando contra los peces aquí!"

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\24_Deep_Water.cfg:487
msgid "Wait for us! We are still fighting the saurians here!"
msgstr "¡Espérennos! ¡Aún estamos luchando contra los saurios aquí!"

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\24_Deep_Water.cfg:499
msgid ""
"I don't think we will be able to pass through both the saurians and the "
"fishes."
msgstr ""
"No creo que podamos pasar a través de tanto los saurios como los peces."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\24_Deep_Water.cfg:503
msgid "We need to find another way."
msgstr "Necesitamos encontrar otra forma."

#. [scenario], id=25_Troll_Cave
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\25_Troll_Cave.cfg:4
msgid "Troll Cave"
msgstr "Cueva de Troll"

#. [side], type=Bay Horse
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\25_Troll_Cave.cfg:421
msgid "Horse"
msgstr "Caballo"

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\25_Troll_Cave.cfg:503
msgid "Wait! I recognize this noise."
msgstr "¡Espera! Reconozco este ruido."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\25_Troll_Cave.cfg:507
msgid ""
"It sounds exactly like the ice troll leader we defeated before entering the "
"ice cave."
msgstr ""
"Suena exactamente como el líder trol de hielo que derrotamos antes de entrar "
"a la cueva de hielo."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\25_Troll_Cave.cfg:511
msgid "But it should be too warm here for the ice trolls?!"
msgstr "¡Pero debería hacer demasiado calor aquí para los trolls de hielo!"

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\25_Troll_Cave.cfg:515
msgid ""
"You are unfortunately right. This cave is full of trolls. Not the ice "
"version, but the normal ones."
msgstr ""
"Lamentablemente tienes razón. Esta cueva está llena de trolls. No la versión "
"de hielo, sino los normales."

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\25_Troll_Cave.cfg:519
msgid ""
"When I withdrew all the legionary patrols that were in duty in the "
"underground caves during the attacks, there’s no doubt the trolls had a "
"field day while they were away."
msgstr ""
"Cuando retiré todas las patrullas legionarias que estaban de servicio en las "
"cuevas subterráneas durante los ataques, sin duda los trolls se dieron un "
"festín mientras estaban ausentes."

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\25_Troll_Cave.cfg:523
msgid ""
"We need to kill the troll leader. That should disorganize them enough that "
"we can easily take back control of the cave later."
msgstr ""
"Tenemos que matar al líder trol. Eso debería desorganizarlos lo suficiente "
"como para que luego podamos retomar el control de la cueva fácilmente."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\25_Troll_Cave.cfg:527
msgid "I am afraid we will have to fight those trolls to continue our journey."
msgstr ""
"Me temo que tendremos que pelear con esos trolls para continuar nuestro "
"viaje."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\25_Troll_Cave.cfg:542
msgid ""
"South: Black Forest\n"
"North: Abxoowbu’s trading post"
msgstr ""
"Sur: Bosque Negro\n"
"Norte: Puesto comercial de Abxoowbu"

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\25_Troll_Cave.cfg:566
msgid ""
"I do not like leaving those trolls roaming the path behind us, but we have a "
"more important mission than dealing with them."
msgstr ""
"No me gusta dejar a esos trolls vagando por el camino detrás de nosotros, "
"pero tenemos una misión más importante que lidiar con ellos."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\25_Troll_Cave.cfg:593
msgid ""
"Now that we dealt with those trolls, the traffic should be able to start "
"again from Udxatfe."
msgstr ""
"Ahora que nos ocupamos de esos trolls, el tráfico debería poder reanudarse "
"desde Udxatfe."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\25_Troll_Cave.cfg:597
msgid "Let's try to find the exit of this cave... and the staff."
msgstr "Intentemos encontrar la salida de esta cueva... y el bastón."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\25_Troll_Cave.cfg:611
msgid "First saurians, then fishes and now trolls."
msgstr "Primero saurios, luego peces y ahora trolls."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\25_Troll_Cave.cfg:615
msgid "That's too much for us. We are not legionaries."
msgstr "Eso es demasiado para nosotros. No somos legionarios."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\25_Troll_Cave.cfg:628
msgid "Hey there, pal. Don't worry, you're safe now."
msgstr "Oye, amigo. No te preocupes, ahora estás a salvo."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\25_Troll_Cave.cfg:632
msgid "That's quite a bad situation you got into. Want to come with us?"
msgstr ""
"Te metiste en una situación bastante mala. ¿Quieres venir con nosotros?"

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\25_Troll_Cave.cfg:662
msgid "There's a horse here."
msgstr "Hay un caballo aquí."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\25_Troll_Cave.cfg:666
msgid "What is it doing here?"
msgstr "¿Qué hace aquí?"

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\25_Troll_Cave.cfg:670
msgid "Maybe it fled from fear and got stuck here?"
msgstr "¿Tal vez huyó del miedo y quedó atrapado aquí?"

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\25_Troll_Cave.cfg:674
msgid "It will not leave long alone here. Maybe we could try to get to it."
msgstr ""
"No va a sobrevivir mucho tiempo solo aquí. Tal vez podríamos intentar "
"acercarnos."

#. [scenario], id=26b_Troll_Fort
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:4
msgid "Troll Fort"
msgstr "Fuerte de Troll"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:50
msgid "Clean the fort"
msgstr "Limpia el fuerte"

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:268
msgid ""
"Those ruins looks weird. They don't look like something trolls would build."
msgstr ""
"Estas ruinas se ven extrañas. No parecen algo que construirían los trolls."

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:278
msgid ""
"They are indeed no troll ruins. This is where the legionary patrols were "
"living in the cave."
msgstr ""
"En efecto, no son ruinas de trolls. Aquí vivían las patrullas legionarias "
"dentro de la cueva."

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:282
msgid ""
"The fort is a bit north.\n"
"It would be good to flush them out of it. Legionaries would then have an "
"easier time coming here to patrol again."
msgstr ""
"El fuerte está un poco al norte.\n"
"Sería bueno sacarlos de ahí. Así los legionarios tendrían más facilidad para "
"volver a patrullar aquí."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:289
msgid ""
"There seems to be some kind of fort further north. I imagine the path goes "
"through it."
msgstr ""
"Parece haber algún tipo de fuerte más al norte. Imagino que el camino pasa "
"por ahí."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:453
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:684
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:791
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:1026
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:1133
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1612
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1704
msgid "There is a lever on the floor. Should I pull it down?"
msgstr "Hay una palanca en el suelo. ¿Debería bajarla?"

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:478
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:701
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:816
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:1043
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:1158
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1664
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1733
msgid "There is a lever on the floor. Should I pull it up?"
msgstr "Hay una palanca en el suelo. ¿Debería subirla?"

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:1203
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:1270
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:1337
msgid "There is a chest. Should I open it?"
msgstr "Hay un cofre. ¿Debería abrirlo?"

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:1217
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:1284
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:1351
msgid "It is empty."
msgstr "Está vacío."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:1233
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:1300
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:1367
msgid "Argh! The chest was trapped."
msgstr "¡Argh! El cofre estaba atrapado."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:1241
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:1308
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:1375
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\30_Bandit_Camp.cfg:442
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\30_Bandit_Camp.cfg:459
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\30_Bandit_Camp.cfg:476 .\utils\macros.cfg:324
msgid "There is something in the chest."
msgstr "Hay algo en el cofre."

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:1248
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:1315
msgid "No, it might be trapped."
msgstr "No, podría estar trampeado."

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:1417
msgid ""
"I think there are no more trolls in there. We can go back to the crossing "
"and take the other path to the exit."
msgstr ""
"Creo que ya no quedan trolls ahí dentro. Podemos volver al cruce y tomar el "
"otro camino hacia la salida."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:1445
msgid ""
"We already spent too much time here. We do not have enough time to clean the "
"whole fort.\n"
"Let's go."
msgstr ""
"Ya pasamos demasiado tiempo aquí. No tenemos tiempo suficiente para limpiar "
"todo el fuerte.\n"
"Vámonos."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:1458
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:1492
msgid ""
"We already spent too much time here. I don't think the exit is this way.\n"
"Let's go back to the crossing and take the other road."
msgstr ""
"Ya pasamos demasiado tiempo aquí. No creo que la salida sea por este lado.\n"
"Volvamos al cruce y tomemos el otro camino."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:1479
msgid ""
"I think there are no more trolls in there. \n"
"Let's go back to the crossing and take the other path to the exit."
msgstr ""
"Creo que ya no quedan trolls ahí dentro. \n"
"Volvamos al cruce y tomemos el otro camino hacia la salida."

#. [scenario], id=26_Echo_Chamber
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26_Echo_Chamber.cfg:4
msgid "Echo Chamber"
msgstr "Cámara de Eco"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26_Echo_Chamber.cfg:24
msgid "Defeat enemy leader"
msgstr "Derrota al líder enemigo"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26_Echo_Chamber.cfg:29
msgid "Defeat all enemies"
msgstr "Derrota a todos los enemigos"

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26_Echo_Chamber.cfg:322
msgid ""
"It sounds like there are more trolls ahead. They must be in a huge room by "
"the echo."
msgstr ""
"Suena como si hubiera más trolls adelante. Deben estar en una sala enorme "
"por el eco."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26_Echo_Chamber.cfg:326
msgid "Anyway, we need to advance. I am sure the exit is not far."
msgstr ""
"De todos modos, tenemos que avanzar. Estoy seguro de que la salida no está "
"lejos."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26_Echo_Chamber.cfg:338
msgid ""
"Oh, I understand the echo now. The chamber is not huge, it is really deep."
msgstr ""
"Ah, ahora entiendo el eco. La cámara no es enorme, es realmente profunda."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26_Echo_Chamber.cfg:351
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26_Echo_Chamber.cfg:465
msgid "The road splits here. We can go north or south."
msgstr "El camino se divide aquí. Podemos ir al norte o al sur."

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26_Echo_Chamber.cfg:362
msgid ""
"The road north leads to the legionaries fort. It is a dead end but I am "
"afraid it is now full of trolls. \n"
"The road south continue to the exit of the cave."
msgstr ""
"El camino al norte lleva al fuerte de los legionarios. Es un callejón sin "
"salida, pero me temo que ahora está lleno de trolls.\n"
"El camino al sur continúa hacia la salida de la cueva."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26_Echo_Chamber.cfg:383
msgid "We should clean the fort before leaving."
msgstr "Deberíamos limpiar el fuerte antes de salir."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26_Echo_Chamber.cfg:389
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26_Echo_Chamber.cfg:477
msgid "Let's go North. That should be the way out."
msgstr "Vamos al Norte. Ese debería ser el camino de salida."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26_Echo_Chamber.cfg:415
msgid "We have no time to clean the fort. Our mission is too urgent."
msgstr ""
"No tenemos tiempo para limpiar el fuerte. Nuestra misión es demasiado "
"urgente."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26_Echo_Chamber.cfg:421
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26_Echo_Chamber.cfg:495
msgid "Let's go South. That should be the way out."
msgstr "Vamos al Sur. Ese debería ser el camino de salida."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26_Echo_Chamber.cfg:459
msgid "It is so quiet now. I think this was the last one."
msgstr "Está tan silencioso ahora. Creo que este fue el último."

#. [scenario], id=27_Saurian_Pond
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:4
msgid "Saurian Pond"
msgstr "Estanque de Saurios"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:26
msgid "Defeat the saurian leader"
msgstr "Derrota al líder saurio"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:31
msgid "Defeat all leaders"
msgstr "Derrota a todos los líderes"

#. [side], type=Purple Crystal LoI
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:162
msgid "Crystals"
msgstr "Cristales"

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:297
msgid ""
"I am a bit worried about letting those trolls behind us. I hope they will "
"not come to stab us in the back."
msgstr ""
"Me preocupa un poco dejar a esos trolls atrás. Espero que no vengan a "
"apuñalarnos por la espalda."

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:307
msgid ""
"I'm afraid we don't have time to worry now. We are now entering the saurian "
"territory."
msgstr ""
"Me temo que no tenemos tiempo para preocuparnos ahora. Estamos entrando al "
"territorio saurio."

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:311
msgid ""
"They might not be as impressive as trolls, but they are fierce warriors."
msgstr ""
"Tal vez no sean tan impresionantes como los trolls, pero son guerreros "
"feroces."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:317
msgid ""
"We do not have time to worry though. We must find the exit of this cave and "
"the protection staff."
msgstr ""
"De todos modos no tenemos tiempo para preocuparnos. Tenemos que encontrar la "
"salida de esta cueva y el bastón de protección."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:326
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:341
msgid "It should be a bit better now that we have killed the troll leaders."
msgstr "Debería estar un poco mejor ahora que matamos a los líderes trolls."

#. [message]
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:330
msgid ""
"I'm however afraid that we might only have killed some of them. There might "
"still be more hidden in the cave we left."
msgstr ""
"Sin embargo, me temo que solo hayamos matado a algunos. Podría haber más "
"escondidos en la cueva que dejamos atrás."

#. [message]
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:334
msgid ""
"However, I do not think this is a good time to think about that. Even if we "
"had killed all trolls in this cave, there are still others enemies awaiting "
"us."
msgstr ""
"Sin embargo, no creo que sea buen momento para pensar en eso. Aunque "
"hubiéramos matado a todos los trolls de esta cueva, todavía nos esperan "
"otros enemigos."

#. [message]
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:345
msgid "This is unfortunately not how it works."
msgstr "Lamentablemente no funciona así."

#. [message]
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:349
msgid ""
"There is now an empty spot in the hierarchy of the cave. The other creatures "
"are going to fight to find out which will take their place."
msgstr ""
"Ahora hay un puesto vacío en la jerarquía de la cueva. Las otras criaturas "
"van a pelear para ver quién toma su lugar."

#. [message]
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:353
msgid "Be prepared to fight aggressive creatures."
msgstr "Prepárense para pelear con criaturas agresivas."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:357
msgid "Wait, you mean we should have left the trolls live."
msgstr "Espera, ¿quieres decir que deberíamos haber dejado vivos a los trolls?"

#. [message]
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:361
msgid ""
"No, we had to deal with them. But now we need to deal with the other "
"creatures. Otherwise the cave will be even more dangerous in the following "
"weeks, the time needed for things to calm down."
msgstr ""
"No, teníamos que ocuparnos de ellos. Pero ahora tenemos que ocuparnos de las "
"otras criaturas. De lo contrario la cueva será aún más peligrosa en las "
"próximas semanas, el tiempo que tome que las cosas se calmen."

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:380
msgid "That's one huge crystal."
msgstr "Ese es un cristal enorme."

#. [message]
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:384
msgid ""
"It looks like it is controlling the other ones. Maybe destroying it would "
"disturb the others for a while."
msgstr ""
"Parece que está controlando a los otros. Tal vez destruirlo los "
"desestabilice por un rato."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:403
msgid "That was a hard fight, but I think we cleaned the cave."
msgstr "Fue una pelea dura, pero creo que limpiamos la cueva."

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:407
msgid "It even looks like this one was guardian a treasure."
msgstr "Incluso parece que este estaba cuidando un tesoro."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:411
msgid ""
"Not that we are doing that for gold, but we might need it for our journey. "
"Take it."
msgstr ""
"No es que lo hagamos por el oro, pero podríamos necesitarlo para el viaje. "
"Tómenlo."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:415
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:445
msgid ""
"I'm glad we finally found the exit. I would not have spent another day in "
"that cave."
msgstr ""
"Me alegra que por fin hayamos encontrado la salida. No habría pasado ni un "
"día más en esa cueva."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:441
msgid ""
"It is a mess here with all those creatures fighting for their small part of "
"this cave."
msgstr ""
"Es un desastre aquí con todas esas criaturas luchando por su pequeña parte "
"de esta cueva."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:449
msgid ""
"Let's leave before they decide that we are more interesting than protecting "
"their territory."
msgstr ""
"Vámonos antes de que decidan que somos más interesantes que proteger su "
"territorio."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:461
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:555
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\29_Black_Forest.cfg:595
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\30_Bandit_Camp.cfg:656
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\31_Corrupted_Temple.cfg:1682
msgid "Wait for us! We are still fighting here!"
msgstr "¡Espérennos! ¡Aún estamos luchando aquí!"

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:474
msgid ""
"There are too many creatures there. Let's go back and try to find another "
"way through the cave."
msgstr ""
"Hay demasiadas criaturas ahí. Volvamos e intentemos encontrar otro camino a "
"través de la cueva."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:491
msgid ""
"North-West: Black Forest\n"
"South-East: Abxoowbu’s trading post"
msgstr ""
"Noroeste: Bosque Negro\n"
"Sureste: Puesto comercial de Abxoowbu"

#. [scenario], id=28_Travelers
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:4
msgid "Travelers"
msgstr "Viajeros"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:38
msgid "Find the camp fire."
msgstr "Encuentra el fuego de campamento."

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:48
msgid "Leave south."
msgstr "Sal al sur."

#. [side], type=Duelist
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:296
msgid "Travellers"
msgstr "Viajeros"

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:403
msgid "Finally back outside. I was getting tired of the trolls."
msgstr "Por fin de vuelta afuera. Ya me estaba cansando de los trolls."

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:413
msgid ""
"Well, now that you mention it, the legion was not only controlling the "
"trolls INSIDE the cave. It was also preventing them from going OUTSIDE the "
"cave."
msgstr ""
"Bueno, ya que lo mencionas, la legión no solo controlaba a los trolls DENTRO "
"de la cueva. También les impedía salir AFUERA de la cueva."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:417
msgid ""
"So what you are telling me is that we should expect more trolls out here, "
"shouldn't we?"
msgstr ""
"Entonces, ¿lo que me estás diciendo es que deberíamos esperar más trolls "
"aquí afuera, no?"

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:421
msgid "I'm afraid so."
msgstr "Me temo que sí."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:425
msgid "What did I do to deserve this?!"
msgstr "¡¿Qué hice yo para merecer esto?!"

#. [message]
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:431
msgid ""
"I'm sorry to be a bummer, but it looks lie there are trolls outside too."
msgstr ""
"Lo siento por ser aguafiestas, pero parece que también hay trolls afuera."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:435
msgid "Oh, come on!"
msgstr "¡Oh, vamos!"

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:441
msgid "Wait, don't you smell smoke?"
msgstr "Espera, ¿no huelen humo?"

#. [1]
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:445
msgid "Could be a distress fire... or a barbecue."
msgstr "Podría ser una fogata de auxilio... o un asado."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:449
msgid "A distress barbecue?"
msgstr "¿Un asado de auxilio?"

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:453
msgid ""
"Anyway, we need to find out if it comes from friends or foes, if it is a "
"good or a bad news."
msgstr ""
"De todos modos, tenemos que averiguar si viene de amigos o enemigos, si son "
"buenas o malas noticias."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:457
msgid "I sure hope it's a barbecue."
msgstr "Seguro espero que sea un asado."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:471
msgid "Who goez there? Friend or foe?"
msgstr "¿Quién va ahí? ¿Amigo o enemigo?"

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:475
msgid "I don't know, who are you?"
msgstr "No sé, ¿quiénes son ustedes?"

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:479
msgid ""
"What do you mean you don't know? Are you ztupid or are you trying to get "
"killed?"
msgstr ""
"¿Qué significa que no sabes? ¿Eres eztúpido o eztoy tratando de que te maten?"

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:483
msgid "We are travellerz? What about you?"
msgstr "¿Somos viajeroz? ¿Y ustedes?"

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:487
msgid ""
"We are a party on a mission for the kingdom of Idaamub. But it is a secret "
"mission."
msgstr ""
"Somos un grupo en una misión para el reino de Idaamub. Pero es una misión "
"secreta."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:491
msgid "Then you're friendz. You might actually even be able to help uz."
msgstr "Entonces zon amigoz. Tal vez incluso puedan ayudarnoz."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:495
msgid ""
"You can get zome rezt in our camp. We could even do some buzinezz if you "
"have zome money or thingz to zell."
msgstr ""
"Pueden tomar algo de rezto en nueztro campamento. Incluso podríamos hacer "
"algunoz negocioz zi tienen algo de dinero o cosaz para vender."

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:499
msgid ""
"We smelled the smoke of your fire from far away. Was it a distress signal?"
msgstr "Olimos el humo de su fogata desde lejos. ¿Era una señal de auxilio?"

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:503
msgid "No, we're juzt grilling some meat."
msgstr "No, zolamente eztamos azando carne."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:507
msgid "I knew it!"
msgstr "¡Lo sabía!"

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:511
msgid ""
"Well, it looks like we found the source of the smell. They don't seem to be "
"in immediate trouble, so I think we can continue as soon as we want."
msgstr ""
"Bueno, parece que encontramos la fuente del olor. No parecen estar en "
"problemas inmediatos, así que creo que podemos continuar cuando queramos."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:539
msgid ""
"My friends, It seems our mission is getting more dangerous. From what we "
"learnt here, we won't have to face only the goblins to get the staff back."
msgstr ""
"Mis amigos, parece que nuestra misión se está volviendo más peligrosa. De lo "
"que aprendimos aquí, no tendremos que enfrentar solo a los goblins para "
"recuperar el bastón."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:543
msgid "Anyway, this cannot stop us, as the destiny of Idaamub is in our hands."
msgstr ""
"De todos modos, esto no puede detenernos, ya que el destino de Idaamub está "
"en nuestras manos."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:565
msgid "Wait a minute. We still need to find where this smell comes from."
msgstr "Espera un minuto. Aún necesitamos encontrar de dónde viene este olor."

#. [message], speaker=Rhadoc
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:582
msgid ""
"It muzt have been written zomewhere that our life will only be zuffering."
msgstr ""
"Debe haber eztado ezcrito en alguna parte que nueztra vida zolo zerá zufri-"
"miento."

#. [message], speaker=Rhadoc
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:590
msgid ""
"The men of our camp are buzy anzwering the bravado of the harmlezz bandits, "
"but I zee emerging a danger far greater than those banditz. Be careful if "
"you go in the zwamp."
msgstr ""
"Loz hombrez de nueztro campamento eztán ocupadaz repondiendo a laz bravataz "
"de loz banditaz inofenzivoz, pero veo que aparece un peligro mucho mayor que "
"eztoz banditaz. Tengan cuidado zi entran al pantano."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:594
msgid "What is the problem?"
msgstr "¿Cuál es el problema?"

#. [message], speaker=Rhadoc
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:598
msgid ""
"During more than a month, my zizterz and I had nightmarez in which we were "
"zeeing an huge army of zoullezz goblinz. There were bowing down before a "
"huge black zymbol of power which waz getting bigger and bigger, fulled by "
"the revenge and the hatred of the abyzz’ demonz. I fear the powerluzt of the "
"goblins cauzez an invazion of the forcez of evil."
msgstr ""
"Durante máz de un mez, mi hermanaz y yo tuvimoz pesadilla en laz que veíamoz "
"un eztructuro ezénormez de goblinzez zin alma. Se inclinaban ante un enorme "
"zímbolo negro de poder que crecía y crecía, alimentado por la venganza y el "
"odio de loz demonioz del abizmo. Temo que la ambición de poder de loz "
"goblinzez cauze una invazión de laz fuerzaz del mal."

#. [message], speaker=Ritharry
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:612
msgid ""
"We are indeed going through a trial. It began with the rapt of our zizter "
"Bta, and now the banditz are threatening to kill uz."
msgstr ""
"En efecto eztamoz paazando por una prueba. Comenzó con el rapto de nueztra "
"hermanaz Bta, y ahora loz banditaz amenazan con matarnoz."

#. [message], speaker=Fdi
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:626
msgid "Evil-eyed creaturez… came… and took my Bta."
msgstr "Criaturaz de ojoz malvadoz… vinieron… y ze llevaron a mi Bta."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:630
msgid "What kind of creatures?"
msgstr "¿Qué clase de criaturas?"

#. [message], speaker=Fdi
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:634
msgid ""
"They look like the horrible Ockz from the legendz… but how could it be "
"pozzible? The Ockz were killed… slaughtered three hundred yearz ago by the "
"first king of your kingdom. "
msgstr ""
"Se parecen a loz horriblez Ockz de laz leyenda… pero ¿cómo podría zer "
"pozible? Loz Ockz fueron matadoz… mazacradoz hace trez cientoz año por el "
"primer rey de zu reino."

#. [message], speaker=Fdi
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:638
msgid ""
"But I am confident my daughter will give them a hard time. She is a… "
"Traveler."
msgstr "Pero eztóy seguro de que mi hija lez dará pelea. Ella ez una… Viajera."

