#. [message], speaker=trader
#. [object]
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\32_Eastern_Swamp.cfg:1917
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1851
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12199
msgid "Great potion of rejuvenation"
msgstr "Gran poción de rejuvenecimiento"

#. [message], speaker=trader
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\32_Eastern_Swamp.cfg:1918
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1852
msgid "Great experience potion"
msgstr "Gran poción de experiencia"

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\32_Eastern_Swamp.cfg:2208
msgid "What's that? This definitely looks weirder that the rest."
msgstr "¿Qué es eso? Esto definitivamente se ve más raro que el resto."

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\32_Eastern_Swamp.cfg:2212
msgid "It looks like a dunefolk but made out of metal."
msgstr "Parece un barján, pero hecho de metal."

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\32_Eastern_Swamp.cfg:2216
msgid "Bloody goblins. They keep stealing our technology and corrupting it."
msgstr "Malditos goblins. Siguen robando nuestra tecnología y corrompiéndola."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\32_Eastern_Swamp.cfg:2220
msgid ""
"Thank Of, this is the sign we were looking for. The lair's entrance should "
"not be far."
msgstr ""
"Gracias a Of, esta es la señal que buscábamos. La entrada a la guarida no "
"debería estar lejos."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\32_Eastern_Swamp.cfg:2233
msgid ""
"There is a massive tree with a huge hole between its roots. It looks like "
"there is a tunnel leading under it."
msgstr ""
"Hay un árbol enorme con un agujero gigante entre sus raíces. Parece que hay "
"un túnel que lleva debajo."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\32_Eastern_Swamp.cfg:2237
msgid "There seems to be an elevator under the tree."
msgstr "Parece que hay un elevador debajo del árbol."

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\32_Eastern_Swamp.cfg:2241
msgid "As I said, always stealing our technology."
msgstr "Como dije, siempre robando nuestra tecnología."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\32_Eastern_Swamp.cfg:2245
msgid "This must be the entrance! Let's go in there!"
msgstr "¡Esta debe ser la entrada! ¡Entremos ahí!"

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\32_Eastern_Swamp.cfg:2259
msgid "Well, no sign of a goblin. It was probably only a rumor."
msgstr "Bueno, ni rastro de un goblin. Probablemente solo era un rumor."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\32_Eastern_Swamp.cfg:2263
msgid "I'm afraid we won't find Teumiuxe's staff in this swamp..."
msgstr "Me temo que no encontraremos el bastón de Teumiuxe en este pantano..."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\32_Eastern_Swamp.cfg:2303
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\32_Eastern_Swamp.cfg:2336
msgid "The house was full of trolls."
msgstr "La casa estaba llena de trolls."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\33_Goblins_Lair.cfg:25
msgid "There was an enemy hidden in this box."
msgstr "Había un enemigo escondido en esta caja."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\33_Goblins_Lair.cfg:59
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\34_Hive.cfg:1607
msgid "The wall was actually a door. There is an enemy inside."
msgstr "La pared en realidad era una puerta. Hay un enemigo dentro."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\33_Goblins_Lair.cfg:99
msgid "The wall was actually a door. There are enemies inside."
msgstr "La pared en realidad era una puerta. Hay enemigos dentro."

#. [scenario], id=33_Goblins_Lair
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\33_Goblins_Lair.cfg:108
msgid "Goblin's Lair"
msgstr "Escondite del Goblin"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\33_Goblins_Lair.cfg:145
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\34_Hive.cfg:54
msgid "Find the protection staff"
msgstr "Encuentra el bastón de protección"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\33_Goblins_Lair.cfg:156
msgid "Kill all goblins"
msgstr "Mata a todos los goblins"

#. [side], type=Goblin Chieftain
#. [side], type=Steel Skewer
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\33_Goblins_Lair.cfg:200
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\34_Hive.cfg:98
msgid "Goblins"
msgstr "Goblins"

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\33_Goblins_Lair.cfg:1566
msgid "I would'nt've expected to find a cave like that under the swamp."
msgstr "No habría esperado encontrar una cueva así debajo del pantano."

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\33_Goblins_Lair.cfg:1570
msgid ""
"That's because we are far underground. We passed the clay layer that is "
"creating the swamp."
msgstr ""
"Eso es porque estamos muy bajo tierra. Pasamos la capa de arcilla que crea "
"el pantano."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\33_Goblins_Lair.cfg:1574
msgid ""
"The good news is that we found the goblins, which means the staff is "
"hopefully not far."
msgstr ""
"La buena noticia es que encontramos a los goblins, lo que significa que el "
"bastón, con suerte, no está lejos."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\33_Goblins_Lair.cfg:1578
msgid ""
"The bad news is that we also found whatever that weird thing up there was. "
"I'm afraid it might not be a one-of-a-kind."
msgstr ""
"La mala noticia es que también encontramos lo que sea que era esa cosa rara "
"de allá arriba. Me temo que no sea algo único en su clase."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\33_Goblins_Lair.cfg:1582
msgid ""
"The goblins seem to be working on them. They may be the ones assembling and "
"reparing them."
msgstr ""
"Los goblins parecen estar trabajando en ellas. Probablemente sean ellos "
"quienes las arman y reparan."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\33_Goblins_Lair.cfg:1602
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\33_Goblins_Lair.cfg:1624
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\34_Hive.cfg:931 .\scenarios\chapter4\34_Hive.cfg:953
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\34_Hive.cfg:995 .\scenarios\chapter4\34_Hive.cfg:1020
msgid "There's a weird-looking orb here. Should I touch it?"
msgstr "Hay una esfera de aspecto extraño aquí. ¿Debería tocarla?"

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\33_Goblins_Lair.cfg:1612
msgid "It looks like it stopped the leak that was spitting fire on the bridge."
msgstr "Parece que detuvo la fuga que estaba escupiendo fuego sobre el puente."

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\33_Goblins_Lair.cfg:1617
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\33_Goblins_Lair.cfg:1643
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\34_Hive.cfg:946 .\scenarios\chapter4\34_Hive.cfg:972
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\34_Hive.cfg:1013 .\scenarios\chapter4\34_Hive.cfg:1046
msgid "No, who knows what it does."
msgstr "No, quién sabe qué hace."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\33_Goblins_Lair.cfg:1638
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\34_Hive.cfg:967
msgid "The fire caused by the leak is back."
msgstr "El fuego causado por la fuga volvió."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\33_Goblins_Lair.cfg:1669
msgid ""
"It looks like there's a leak in a big pipe passing over the bridge that is "
"causing a fire. We need to find a way to stop it if we don't want to burn "
"going on the bridge."
msgstr ""
"Parece que hay una fuga en una tubería grande que pasa sobre el puente y "
"está causando un incendio. Necesitamos encontrar una forma de detenerla si "
"no queremos quemarnos al cruzar el puente."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\33_Goblins_Lair.cfg:1707
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\33_Goblins_Lair.cfg:1750
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\34_Hive.cfg:1087 .\scenarios\chapter4\34_Hive.cfg:1130
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\34_Hive.cfg:1172 .\scenarios\chapter4\34_Hive.cfg:1215
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\34_Hive.cfg:1257 .\scenarios\chapter4\34_Hive.cfg:1300
msgid "Argh! I'm burning!"
msgstr "¡Argh! ¡Me quemo!"

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\33_Goblins_Lair.cfg:1775
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\33_Goblins_Lair.cfg:1878
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\33_Goblins_Lair.cfg:2089
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\33_Goblins_Lair.cfg:2132
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\33_Goblins_Lair.cfg:2175
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\33_Goblins_Lair.cfg:2218
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\33_Goblins_Lair.cfg:2261
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\33_Goblins_Lair.cfg:2388
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\33_Goblins_Lair.cfg:2431
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\34_Hive.cfg:1325 .\scenarios\chapter4\34_Hive.cfg:1368
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\34_Hive.cfg:1411 .\scenarios\chapter4\34_Hive.cfg:1454
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\34_Hive.cfg:1497 .\scenarios\chapter4\34_Hive.cfg:1544
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\34_Hive.cfg:1686
msgid "There's a huge metal door. Should I open it?"
msgstr "Hay una puerta enorme de metal. ¿Debería abrirla?"

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\33_Goblins_Lair.cfg:1820
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\33_Goblins_Lair.cfg:2312
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\33_Goblins_Lair.cfg:2365
msgid "A machine came out of a trap."
msgstr "Una máquina salió de una trampa."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\33_Goblins_Lair.cfg:1853
msgid "Two machines came out of a trap."
msgstr "Dos máquinas salieron de una trampa."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\33_Goblins_Lair.cfg:1963
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\33_Goblins_Lair.cfg:2017
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\33_Goblins_Lair.cfg:2050
msgid "The bridge turned."
msgstr "El puente giró."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\33_Goblins_Lair.cfg:1982
msgid "The door also opened."
msgstr "La puerta también se abrió."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\33_Goblins_Lair.cfg:2342
msgid "The wall was actually a door. There is something inside."
msgstr "La pared en realidad era una puerta. Hay algo dentro."

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\33_Goblins_Lair.cfg:2471
msgid "Look over there. This one looks a bit like a dwarf."
msgstr "Miren allá. Este se parece un poco a un enano."

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\33_Goblins_Lair.cfg:2478
msgid "Kill it! Burn it! Destroy it!!!"
msgstr "¡Mátenlo! ¡Quemenlo! ¡Destrúyanlo!"

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\33_Goblins_Lair.cfg:2482
msgid "The whole place! Make it explode!!!"
msgstr "¡Todo el lugar! ¡Hagan que explote!"

#. [message]
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\33_Goblins_Lair.cfg:2486
msgid ""
"They look quite dangerous. It might be a good idea to kill the goblins "
"servicing them to prevent them from being repaired."
msgstr ""
"Se ven bastante peligrosos. Podría ser buena idea matar a los goblins que "
"los atienden para evitar que los reparen."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\33_Goblins_Lair.cfg:2512
msgid "Great... Another elevator..."
msgstr "Genial... Otro elevador..."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\33_Goblins_Lair.cfg:2516
msgid ""
"I assume this means that we need to go deeper to find the goblin leader. And "
"the staff."
msgstr ""
"Asumo que esto significa que tenemos que bajar más profundo para encontrar "
"al líder goblin. Y el bastón."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\33_Goblins_Lair.cfg:2536
msgid "Let's go down. We need to find the goblin leader. And the staff."
msgstr "Bajemos. Necesitamos encontrar al líder goblin. Y el bastón."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\33_Goblins_Lair.cfg:2548
msgid "Wait for us! We are still fighting the machines here!"
msgstr "¡Espérennos! ¡Aún estamos luchando contra las máquinas aquí!"

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\33_Goblins_Lair.cfg:2572
msgid ""
"It looks like the machines around here stopped. This goblin must have has "
"some king of switch on him."
msgstr ""
"Parece que las máquinas por aquí se detuvieron. Este goblin debe tener algún "
"tipo de interruptor con él."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\33_Goblins_Lair.cfg:2576
msgid "We should be able to continue without being attacked from behind."
msgstr "Deberíamos poder continuar sin ser atacados por la espalda."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\33_Goblins_Lair.cfg:2602
msgid ""
"No sign of the staff. The rumor about the goblins having the staff must have "
"been only a rumor."
msgstr ""
"Ni rastro del bastón. El rumor de que los goblins tenían el bastón debió ser "
"solo un rumor."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\33_Goblins_Lair.cfg:2606
msgid "We need to start again the investigation."
msgstr "Tenemos que volver a empezar la investigación."

#. [scenario], id=34_Hive
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\34_Hive.cfg:4
msgid "Hive"
msgstr "Colmena"

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\34_Hive.cfg:907
msgid ""
"There are a lot of Gobots here. We must be getting close to the goblin "
"leader."
msgstr "Hay muchos Gobots aquí. Debemos estar acercándonos al líder goblin."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\34_Hive.cfg:911
msgid ""
"From what we know, if we find him, we find the sceptre. Let's start "
"searching."
msgstr ""
"Por lo que sabemos, si lo encontramos a él, encontramos el cetro. Empecemos "
"a buscar."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\34_Hive.cfg:941
msgid "It looks like it stopped the leak that was spitting fire from the wall."
msgstr "Parece que detuvo la fuga que estaba escupiendo fuego desde la pared."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\34_Hive.cfg:1008
msgid "It looks like it stopped the leaks that were spitting fire in the room."
msgstr ""
"Parece que detuvo las fugas que estaban escupiendo fuego en la habitación."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\34_Hive.cfg:1041
msgid "The fire caused by the leaks is back."
msgstr "El fuego causado por las fugas volvió."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\34_Hive.cfg:1515
msgid "That part of the tunnel looks abandoned."
msgstr "Esa parte del túnel parece abandonada."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\34_Hive.cfg:1641
msgid "Isn't that one of those dwarvish teleporter?"
msgstr "¿No es ese uno de esos teletransportadores enanos?"

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\34_Hive.cfg:1645
msgid ""
"I'm not even angry. \n"
"I'm being so sincere right now. \n"
"Even though it breaks my heart. \n"
"I'll kill them. \n"
"And tear them to pieces. \n"
"And throw every piece into a fire."
msgstr ""
"Ni siquiera estoy enojado.\n"
"Estoy siendo muy sincero ahora.\n"
"Aunque me parte el corazón.\n"
"Los mataré.\n"
"Los destrozaré en pedazos.\n"
"Y arrojaré cada pedazo al fuego."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\34_Hive.cfg:1654
msgid ""
"How did they even manage to bring it here? It even seems to work. Or at "
"least it's glowing."
msgstr ""
"¿Cómo lograron siquiera traerlo aquí? Incluso parece que funciona. O al "
"menos está brillando."

#. [message]
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\34_Hive.cfg:1658
msgid ""
"You all don't realize. It should not even be possible. One should not be "
"able to move those runes without breaking them or the spell. That's not how "
"magic works."
msgstr ""
"Ustedes no se dan cuenta. Ni siquiera debería ser posible. No se debería "
"poder mover esas runas sin romperlas o romper el hechizo. Así no funciona la "
"magia."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\34_Hive.cfg:1662
msgid ""
"I mean, it's not like if goblins were well known for using things that can "
"malfunction or explode anytime, right?"
msgstr ""
"Quiero decir, no es como si los goblins fueran conocidos por usar cosas que "
"pueden fallar o explotar en cualquier momento, ¿verdad?"

#. [message], speaker=Fe
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\34_Hive.cfg:1709
msgid "Cursed orcs! Cursed invaders!"
msgstr "¡Orcos malditos! ¡Invasores malditos!"

#. [message], speaker=Fe
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\34_Hive.cfg:1713
msgid "Everything rampaged! Fe’s hordes destroyed! "
msgstr "¡Todo arrasado! ¡Las hordas de Fe destruidas!"

#. [message], speaker=Fe
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\34_Hive.cfg:1724
msgid "Ock not have magical staff! Stupid human mage not have staff! "
msgstr "¡Ock no tiene bastón mágico! ¡Mago humano estúpido no tiene bastón!"

#. [message], speaker=Fe
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\34_Hive.cfg:1770
msgid "Protection staff ours! Goblins! You all pay!"
msgstr "¡Bastón de protección nuestro! ¡Goblins! ¡Todos pagan!"

#. [message], speaker=Fe
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\34_Hive.cfg:1793
msgid "Me lose but no problem! Ancient evil and humans fight now!"
msgstr "¡Yo pierdo pero no hay problema! ¡Mal antiguo y humanos pelean ahora!"

#. [message], speaker=Fe
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\34_Hive.cfg:1797
msgid "Goblins look, laugh and take what’s left! Hahaha!"
msgstr "¡Goblins miran, ríen y toman lo que queda! ¡Jajaja!"

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\34_Hive.cfg:1820
msgid ""
"There is some kind of force field preventing me from getting closer to the "
"sceptre."
msgstr ""
"Hay algún tipo de campo de fuerza que me impide acercarme más al cetro."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\34_Hive.cfg:1841
msgid "Here it is. The staff of protection."
msgstr "Aquí está. El bastón de protección."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\34_Hive.cfg:1849
msgid ""
"It seems like removing it from its base shut down the complex. At least we "
"won't have to fight those metal things anymore."
msgstr ""
"Parece que al sacarlo de su base se apagó todo el complejo. Al menos ya no "
"tendremos que pelear con esas cosas de metal."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\34_Hive.cfg:1853
msgid "Hurrah! We have saved Idaamub!"
msgstr "¡Hurra! ¡Hemos salvado a Idaamub!"

#. [message]
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\34_Hive.cfg:1868
msgid "Not so fast young man. I am afraid this goblin gave us dark news."
msgstr "No tan rápido, joven. Me temo que este goblin nos dio malas noticias."

#. [message]
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\34_Hive.cfg:1872
msgid ""
"I would seem that the Ocks have survived and are trying once again to "
"destroy Idaamub."
msgstr ""
"Parece que los Ocks sobrevivieron y están intentando una vez más destruir "
"Idaamub."

#. [message]
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\34_Hive.cfg:1876
msgid ""
"We need to get to the capital and warn the king before it is too late. Our "
"journey has not come to its end yet."
msgstr ""
"Tenemos que llegar a la capital y advertir al rey antes de que sea demasiado "
"tarde. Nuestro viaje aún no ha terminado."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\34_Hive.cfg:1948
msgid ""
"It is so frustrating. I feel we are close to finding the sceptre, but these "
"goblins and their machines won't allow us to get it back."
msgstr ""
"Es tan frustrante. Siento que estamos cerca de encontrar el cetro, pero "
"estos goblins y sus máquinas no nos dejan recuperarlo."

#. [scenario], id=35b_Flooded_Tunnels
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:4
msgid "Flooded Tunnels"
msgstr "Túneles inundados"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:51
msgid "Explore the tunnels"
msgstr "Explorar los túneles"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:65
msgid "Find the treasure hunters"
msgstr "Encontrar a los cazatesoros"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:79
msgid "Report back to Oboavlidlu"
msgstr "Regresar a informar a Oboavlidlu"

#. [side], type=Saurian Matriarch LoI
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:143
msgid "Matriarch"
msgstr "Matriarca"

#. [side], type=Bay Horse
#. [side], type=Pikeman
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:813
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:641
msgid "Humans"
msgstr "Humanos"

#. [unit], id=Papyrus, type=Bay Horse
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:818
msgid "Papyrus"
msgstr "Papyrus"

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:958
msgid "Looks like those tunnels have been abandonned for a while."
msgstr "Parece que estos túneles llevan un buen rato abandonados."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:962
msgid ""
"On the other hand, I don't see much dust, so it seems we are not the first "
"ones going there, humans or creatures."
msgstr ""
"Por otro lado, no veo mucho polvo, así que parece que no somos los primeros "
"en pasar por aquí, ya sean humanos o criaturas."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:966
msgid "Lets look for a way out and hope it takes us closer to our goal."
msgstr "Busquemos una salida y esperemos que nos acerque a nuestro objetivo."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:972
msgid ""
"So those are the famous flooded tunnels. They don't look so flooded from "
"here, although the air is quite moist."
msgstr ""
"Entonces estos son los famosos túneles inundados. No parecen tan inundados "
"desde aquí, aunque el aire está bastante húmedo."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:976
msgid ""
"Our goal is to find the treasure hunters and then report back to Oboavlidlu."
msgstr ""
"Nuestro objetivo es encontrar a los cazadores de tesoros y luego informar a "
"Oboavlidlu."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:980
msgid "Let's make it quick, our main mission is of dire importance."
msgstr "Hagámoslo rápido, nuestra misión principal es de vital importancia."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1003
msgid "This wall looks more recent. Should I tried to demolish it?"
msgstr "Esta pared parece más reciente. ¿Debería intentar demolerla?"

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1017
msgid "Looks like there's a room on the other side. "
msgstr "Parece que hay una habitación del otro lado."

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1022
msgid "We don't have the tools for that."
msgstr "No tenemos las herramientas para eso."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1046
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1089
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1132
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1175
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1290
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1346
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1402
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1527
msgid "There is a huge metal door. Should I open it?"
msgstr "Hay una puerta enorme de metal. ¿Debería abrirla?"

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1065
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1108
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1151
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1194
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1266
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1322
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1378
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1421
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1546
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1657
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1675
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1726
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1744
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1896
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1932
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1968
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:2004
msgid "No, not right now."
msgstr "No, ahora no."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1223
msgid "There are two huge metal doors. Should I open them?"
msgstr "Hay dos puertas enormes de metal. ¿Debería abrirlas?"

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1261
msgid "There're opened."
msgstr "Están abiertas."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1437
msgid "There're corpses in there."
msgstr "Hay cadáveres ahí dentro."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1447
msgid ""
"I'm afraid they are those of the treasure hunter we were supposed to look "
"for. They were probably killed by the saurians."
msgstr ""
"Me temo que son los de los cazadores de tesoros que debíamos buscar. "
"Probablemente fueron asesinados por los saurios."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1451
msgid ""
"Let's go back to the surface and warn Oboavlidlu so that he can give them a "
"decent burial."
msgstr ""
"Volvamos a la superficie y avisemos a Oboavlidlu para que pueda darles un "
"entierro decente."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1458
msgid "Poor fellows. It looks like they were killed by the saurians."
msgstr "Pobres muchachos. Parece que fueron asesinados por los saurios."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1464
msgid ""
"It looks like one of their horses survived though. Maybe we could take him "
"with us?"
msgstr ""
"Sin embargo, parece que uno de sus caballos sobrevivió. ¿Tal vez podríamos "
"llevarlo con nosotros?"

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1503
msgid "No, leave it be. It might be someone's horse."
msgstr "No, déjalo. Podría ser el caballo de alguien."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1570
msgid "It looks like this wall is made of earth. Should I try to dig through?"
msgstr "Parece que esta pared es de tierra. ¿Debería intentar cavar a través?"

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1584
msgid "There seems to be a corridor behind."
msgstr "Parece que hay un corredor detrás."

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1589
msgid "No, we don't have the tools for that."
msgstr "No, no tenemos las herramientas para eso."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1644
msgid "A second lever appear on the floor."
msgstr "Apareció una segunda palanca en el suelo."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1650
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1670
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1739
msgid "It's blocked."
msgstr "Está bloqueada."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1721
msgid "Part of the opposite wall slid down."
msgstr "Parte de la pared opuesta se deslizó hacia abajo."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1765
msgid "What's that?"
msgstr "¿Qué es eso?"

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1780
msgid "Goblin contraption, that's what it's. Let me grab my hammer."
msgstr "Un artefacto goblin, eso es lo que es. Déjame agarrar mi martillo."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1784
msgid "Wait! What's the purpose of it?"
msgstr "¡Espera! ¿Para qué sirve?"

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1788
msgid "Who cares? I say we remove it for the undersurface of the earth."
msgstr ""
"¿A quién le importa? Yo digo que lo saquemos de la superficie de la tierra."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1792
msgid "Amin..."
msgstr "Amin..."

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1796
msgid ""
"Ok, ok. It looks like a giant steam engine. And it looks like it is running. "
"I have no idea what it powers though."
msgstr ""
"Está bien, está bien. Parece un motor de vapor gigante. Y parece que está "
"funcionando. Aunque no tengo idea de qué alimenta."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1800
msgid "What's a steam engine?"
msgstr "¿Qué es un motor de vapor?"

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1804
msgid ""
"A device that produces mechanical energy with water and fire. But I would in "
"no way trust one of goblin fabrication, it could explode anytime, killing "
"everyone in the tunnels."
msgstr ""
"Un dispositivo que produce energía mecánica con agua y fuego. Pero de "
"ninguna manera confiaría en uno fabricado por goblins, podría explotar en "
"cualquier momento y matar a todos en los túneles."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1808
msgid "But you understand how it works, don't you?"
msgstr "Pero tú entiendes cómo funciona, ¿verdad?"

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1812
msgid ""
"I know how a normal one works, not the weird goblin death machines. But I "
"can have a look if you want. It will not be said that a dwarf will fail to "
"understand how an engine works, be it a goblin one."
msgstr ""
"Sé cómo funciona uno normal, no estas extrañas máquinas mortales goblin. "
"Pero puedo echarle un vistazo si quieren. No se dirá que un enano falló en "
"entender cómo funciona un motor, aunque sea uno goblin."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1816
msgid "Please do."
msgstr "Por favor, hazlo."

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1838
msgid ""
"I have never seen such a terrible job at making an engine. I have no idea "
"how it has not exploded yet. I assume the numerous leaks prevent the "
"pressure from rising high enough to do so.\n"
"Anyway, if you really want to make it do whatever it is supposed to, you "
"should turn the four big wheel that are placed on each side of the engine. "
"Then Of bless us for what will happen."
msgstr ""
"Nunca vi un trabajo tan terrible al construir un motor. No tengo idea de "
"cómo no ha explotado todavía. Supongo que las numerosas fugas evitan que la "
"presión suba lo suficiente como para hacerlo.\n"
"De todos modos, si realmente quieren que haga lo que se supone que debe "
"hacer, deberían girar las cuatro ruedas grandes que están en cada lado del "
"motor. Entonces que Of nos bendiga por lo que pase."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1849
msgid ""
"It looks a bit like the goblin engines. I wonder what it does and how it "
"ended up here."
msgstr ""
"Se parece un poco a los motores goblin. Me pregunto qué hace y cómo terminó "
"aquí."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1853
msgid "It looks like there some kind of big wheel on each side."
msgstr "Parece que hay una especie de rueda grande a cada lado."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1857
msgid "Maybe something will happen if we turn each of them."
msgstr "Tal vez pase algo si giramos cada una."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1883
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1919
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1955
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1991
msgid "There is a huge wheel. Should I turn it?"
msgstr "Hay una rueda enorme. ¿Debería girarla?"

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:2021
msgid "Should we go?"
msgstr "¿Deberíamos irnos?"

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:2053
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:2332
msgid "Yes, we are wasting our time here."
msgstr "Sí, estamos perdiendo tiempo aquí."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:2057
msgid "Let's go back and take the main road instead."
msgstr "Volvamos y tomemos el camino principal en su lugar."

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:2097
msgid "No, I am sure there is another exit."
msgstr "No, estoy seguro de que hay otra salida."

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:2132
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:2556
msgid "Yes, this exit should bring us closer to our goal."
msgstr "Sí, esta salida debería acercarnos a nuestro objetivo."

#. [unit], id=trader, type=Rogue
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:2180
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:2388
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:2608
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:2812
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:661
msgid "Oddaty, the Scavenger"
msgstr "Oddaty, el Carroñero"

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:2249
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:2689
msgid "Well, it looks like I was wrong, this was not a shortcut."
msgstr "Bueno, parece que me equivoqué, esto no era un atajo."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:2253
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:2693
msgid ""
"I have been misled by all the tunnels and caves we have used as shortcut or "
"detour since the beginning of our journey."
msgstr ""
"Me dejé llevar por todos los túneles y cuevas que hemos usado como atajo o "
"desvío desde el comienzo de nuestro viaje."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:2257
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:2697
msgid "Let's continue on the main road instead."
msgstr "Sigamos por el camino principal en su lugar."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:2336
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:2953
msgid "There is no sign of the treasure hunters and our mission is urgent."
msgstr "No hay rastro de los cazadores de tesoros y nuestra misión es urgente."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:2340
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:2959
msgid "Let's go back and continue down the old temple road."
msgstr "Volvamos y sigamos por el camino del viejo templo."

#. [message], speaker=Oboavlidlu
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:2469
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:2701
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:2893
msgid "Back already? Have you found the treasure hunters?"
msgstr "¿Ya volvieron? ¿Encontraron a los cazadores de tesoros?"

#. [message]
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:2473
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:2705
msgid ""
"I'm sorry but we've seen no sign of that and we have to time to look longer "
"after then."
msgstr ""
"Lo siento, pero no vimos ningún rastro de ellos y no tenemos tiempo para "
"buscarlos más."

#. [message], speaker=Oboavlidlu
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:2477
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:2709
msgid ""
"I understand. Still, I hope we will find out what happened to them. In these "
"difficult times, it would be regrettable to lose their... support."
msgstr ""
"Entiendo. Aun así, espero que descubramos qué les pasó. En estos tiempos "
"difíciles, sería lamentable perder su... apoyo."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:2481
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:2713
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:2916
msgid "Goodbye. Now, let's continue our journey down the old temple road."
msgstr "Adiós. Ahora, sigamos nuestro viaje por el camino del viejo templo."

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:2521
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:2753
msgid "No, we have not found the treasure hunters yet."
msgstr "No, todavía no encontramos a los cazadores de tesoros."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:2560
msgid ""
"There is no sign of the treasure hunters and our mission is too urgent to "
"waste more time here."
msgstr ""
"No hay rastro de los cazadores de tesoros y nuestra misión es demasiado "
"urgente para perder más tiempo aquí."

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:2764
msgid "Yes, we should go report to Oboavlidlu."
msgstr "Sí, deberíamos ir a informar a Oboavlidlu."

#. [message]
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:2897
msgid "I'm sorry but they are dead."
msgstr "Lo siento, pero están muertos."

#. [message], speaker=Oboavlidlu
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:2901
msgid ""
"You found them dead? That’s marvelous!... Hmm... It is a bit unfortunate."
msgstr ""
"¿Los encontraron muertos? ¡Eso es maravilloso!... Hmm... Es un poco "
"desafortunado."

#. [message], speaker=Oboavlidlu
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:2905
msgid ""
"I knew they were not the kind to leave without saying goodbye. Please take "
"this modest sum in return for your help."
msgstr ""
"Sabía que no eran de los que se van sin despedirse. Por favor, tomen esta "
"modesta suma a cambio de su ayuda."

#. [message], speaker=Oboavlidlu
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:2912
msgid ""
"Oddaty and I will have to go there without delay to make sure to provide "
"a... hmm... decent burial to those poor lads."
msgstr ""
"Oddaty y yo tendremos que ir allá sin demora para asegurarnos de darles "
"un... hmm... entierro decente a esos pobres muchachos."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:2943
msgid "We are wasting our time here."
msgstr "Estamos perdiendo tiempo aquí."

#. [scenario], id=35_Scavengers_Trading_Post
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:4
msgid "Scavenger's Trading Post"
msgstr "Puesto Comercial del Carroñero"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:45
msgid "Find out where you are"
msgstr "Averigua dónde estás"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:55
msgid "Go down the old temple road to Oof foretress."
msgstr "Baja por el camino del templo antiguo a la fortaleza de Oof."

#. [side], type=Foul Dark Wose LoI
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:97
msgid "Dark Woses"
msgstr "Woses Oscuros"

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:717
msgid ""
"The elevator lead us here. I have no idea were we are. I hope we are no too "
"far from an exit."
msgstr ""
"El elevador nos trajo aquí. No tengo idea de dónde estamos. Espero que no "
"estemos muy lejos de una salida."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:721
msgid ""
"It looks like there are some machines further, but they don't seem to move. "
"They probably got disabled with the rest of the complex."
msgstr ""
"Parece que hay algunas máquinas más adelante, pero no parecen moverse. "
"Probablemente se desactivaron junto con el resto del complejo."

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:730
msgid "I gonna smash'em."
msgstr "Voy a destrozarlas."

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:795
msgid "There seem to be a lever there. I gonna pull it."
msgstr "Parece que hay una palanca ahí. Voy a jalarla."

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:812
msgid ""
"A huge rock slid and opened a hole in the wall. It seems I found the exit."
msgstr ""
"Una roca enorme se deslizó y abrió un agujero en la pared. Parece que "
"encontré la salida."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:832
msgid "Pull it please."
msgstr "Jálala por favor."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:848
msgid "A huge rock slid and opened a hole in the wall."
msgstr "Una roca enorme se deslizó y abrió un agujero en la pared."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:852
msgid "It seems we found the exit."
msgstr "Parece que encontramos la salida."

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:862
msgid "Wait, those are legionaries. Let me talk to them."
msgstr "Espera, esos son legionarios. Déjame hablar con ellos."

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:886
msgid "Legionary, report!"
msgstr "¡Legionario, informe!"

#. [message], speaker=Durissa
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:890
msgid "The Great Mage!"
msgstr "¡El Gran Mago!"

#. [message], speaker=Durissa
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:894
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:964
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1026
msgid "By Of’s shield, is the Guardian sending you?"
msgstr "¿Por el escudo de Of, el Guardián te envía?"

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:898
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:968
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1030
msgid ""
"Actually, we are on a mission for the kingdom, but we might be of mutual "
"help."
msgstr ""
"En realidad estamos en una misión para el reino, pero podríamos ayudarnos "
"mutuamente."

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:902
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:972
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1034
msgid "Tell me, where are we and what are you doing here?"
msgstr "Dime, ¿dónde estamos y qué hacen aquí?"

#. [message], speaker=Durissa
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:906
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:976
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1038
msgid ""
"Unfortunately, we are in the middle of nowhere. Our detachment left Oof "
"fortress to try to get emergency reinforcement from Udxatfe."
msgstr ""
"Desafortunadamente, estamos en medio de la nada. Nuestro destacamento dejó "
"la fortaleza de Oof para intentar obtener refuerzos de emergencia de Udxatfe."

#. [message], speaker=Durissa
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:910
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:980
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1042
msgid ""
"Four days ago, a necromancer with terrible powers by the name of Isut "
"appeared and fell onto us, flanked by undead and Dunefolk. The Dunefolk "
"outnumbering us, they blocked access to Idaamub’s castle from the east and "
"we got blocked from both sides."
msgstr ""
"Hace cuatro días, un nigromante con poderes terribles llamado Isut apareció "
"y cayó sobre nosotros, flanqueado por no-muertos y Barjanes. Los Barjanes "
"superándonos en número, bloquearon el acceso al castillo de Idaamub desde el "
"este y nos bloquearon de ambos lados."

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#. [message]
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:914
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:984
msgid "That is terrible news."
msgstr "Eso son terribles noticias."

#. [message], speaker=Durissa
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:918
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:988
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1050
msgid ""
"The six of us left by the old temple road to dodge Isut, but we fell onto "
"one of his tentacle guardians, which did not spare us. We both took refuge "
"here, but it is impossible to bring reinforcement from the legion to captain "
"Soimaql on time."
msgstr ""
"Los seis salimos por el camino del templo antiguo para esquivar a Isut, pero "
"caímos en uno de sus guardianes tentáculo, que no nos perdonó. Ambos nos "
"refugiamos aquí, pero es imposible llevar refuerzos de la legión al capitán "
"Soimaql a tiempo."

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#. [message]
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:922
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:992
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1054
msgid "We might be able to do something about that."
msgstr "Tal vez podamos hacer algo al respecto."

#. [message], speaker=Durissa
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:926
msgid ""
"I know who you are, I think you should be a match for Isut. You could give "
"my comrades the boost they need to stop this monster before he kills us all."
msgstr ""
"Sé quién eres, creo que deberías ser un rival para Isut. Podrías dar a mis "
"camaradas el impulso que necesitan para detener a este monstruo antes de que "
"nos mate a todos."

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#. [message]
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:930
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1000
msgid "Our course of action is clear."
msgstr "Nuestro curso de acción está claro."

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#. [message]
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:934
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1004
msgid ""
"We need to go down the old temple road to reach Oof's fortress and free it "
"from Isut."
msgstr ""
"Tenemos que bajar por el camino del viejo templo para llegar a la fortaleza "
"de Oof y liberarla de Isut."

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#. [message]
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:938
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1008
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1066
msgid "We will then join Idaamub's castle to help break the Dunefolk siege."
msgstr ""
"Luego nos uniremos al castillo de Idaamub para ayudar a romper el asedio de "
"los barjanes."

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#. [message]
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:942
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1012
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1070
msgid "Once it is done, we will be able to deliver our message to the king."
msgstr "Una vez hecho eso, podremos entregar nuestro mensaje al rey."

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#. [message]
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:946
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1016
msgid "Stay here to heal your wounds. You will be of no help like that."
msgstr "Quédense aquí a sanar sus heridas. Así no serán de ayuda."

#. [message], speaker=Durissa
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:950
msgid "Sir, yes, Sir!"
msgstr "¡Señor, sí, señor!"

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:960
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1022
msgid "Excuse me, sir."
msgstr "Disculpe, señor."

#. [message], speaker=Durissa
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:996
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1058
msgid ""
"I don’t know who you are, but if you’re as competent as you look like, I "
"think you should be a match for Isut. You could give my comrades the boost "
"they need to stop this monster before he kills us all."
msgstr ""
"No sé quién eres, pero si eres tan competente como pareces, creo que "
"deberías ser un rival para Isut. Podrías dar a mis camaradas el impulso que "
"necesitan para detener a este monstruo antes de que nos mate a todos."

#. [message]
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1046
msgid "That's terrible news."
msgstr "Eso son terribles noticias."

#. [message]
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1062
msgid ""
"Well, looks like we need to go down the old temple road to reach Oof's "
"fortress and free it from Isut."
msgstr ""
"Bueno, parece que tenemos que bajar por el camino del viejo templo para "
"llegar a la fortaleza de Oof y liberarla de Isut."

#. [message], speaker=Alealyan
#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1093
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\37_Old_Temple.cfg:723
msgid ""
"Those tentacles, those teeth… those flickering lights… and all those dead… "
"why so many dead?"
msgstr ""
"Esos tentáculos, esos dientes… esas luces parpadeantes… y todos esos "
"muertos… ¿por qué tantos muertos?"

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1097
msgid "Looks like he lost his mind."
msgstr "Parece que perdió la cabeza."

#. [message], speaker=Oboavlidlu
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1111
msgid ""
"Mylord Oddaty and I supplied a group of treasure hunters that were examining "
"the flooded tunnels west. Maybe you are also going in that direction?"
msgstr ""
"Mi señor Oddaty y yo abastecimos a un grupo de cazadores de tesoros que "
"estaban explorando los túneles inundados al oeste. ¿Tal vez ustedes también "
"van en esa dirección?"

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1115
msgid "I'm sorry but we aren't."
msgstr "Lo siento, pero no."

#. [message], speaker=Oboavlidlu
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1119
msgid "They have not come for several days. They never talked about leaving."
msgstr "No han venido en varios días. Nunca hablaron de irse."

#. [message], speaker=Oboavlidlu
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1123
msgid ""
"It is always displeasing to lose regular customers, especially when you do "
"not know where they went. If by chance you meet them, tell them we "
"appreciate doing business with them."
msgstr ""
"Siempre es desagradable perder clientes habituales, especialmente cuando no "
"se sabe a dónde fueron. Si por casualidad los encuentran, díganles que "
"apreciamos hacer negocios con ellos."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1127
msgid ""
"Well, if we happen to meet them, we will tell them you are looking forward "
"seeing them again."
msgstr ""
"Bueno, si llegamos a encontrarlos, les diremos que están esperando verlos de "
"nuevo."

#. [message], speaker=Oboavlidlu
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1131
msgid ""
"And if it happens that they… hmm… closed their account, come back to tell us "
"where they are."
msgstr ""
"Y si resulta que ellos… hmm… cerraron su cuenta, vuelvan a decirnos dónde "
"están."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1135
msgid ""
"I am sorry, but, even if we were to visit those tunnels, I do not think we "
"would have the time to come back to you."
msgstr ""
"Lo siento, pero aunque visitáramos esos túneles, no creo que tengamos tiempo "
"de volver aquí."

#. [message], speaker=Oboavlidlu
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1139
msgid ""
"You would not regret it, I promise. In these difficult times, it would be "
"regrettable to lose their… support."
msgstr ""
"No se arrepentirían, se los prometo. En estos tiempos difíciles, sería "
"lamentable perder su… apoyo."

#. [message], speaker=Oboavlidlu
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1143
msgid ""
"Were I to learn that you go into the tunnels, I would wait for you at their "
"entrance; that way you will not have to come back here."
msgstr ""
"Si llegara a enterarme de que van a los túneles, los esperaría en la "
"entrada; así no tendrían que volver aquí."

#. [message], speaker=trader
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1159
msgid ""
"Come in, come in! Hmm… you do not seem move in the best circles, but one "
"should never under-estimate the lower classes…"
msgstr ""
"¡Pasen, pasen! Hmm… no parecen moverse en los mejores círculos, pero nunca "
"se debe subestimar a las clases bajas…"

#. [message], speaker=trader
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1163
msgid ""
"My assistant and I have found these items on a group of mages on the temple "
"road. Some of these items might interest you, but we have not yet got them "
"rid of their… unpleasant smell."
msgstr ""
"Mi asistente y yo encontramos estos objetos en un grupo de magos en el "
"camino del templo. Algunos de estos objetos podrían interesarles, pero aún "
"no hemos logrado quitarles su… olor desagradable."

#. [message], speaker=trader
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1167
msgid "But it should not disturb someone like you, should it?"
msgstr "Pero eso no debería molestar a alguien como ustedes, ¿verdad?"

#. [message], speaker=trader
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1208
msgid "What can Oddaty the Scavenger do for you today?"
msgstr "¿Qué puede hacer Oddaty el Carroñero por ustedes hoy?"

