#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:6571
msgid ""
"Politics is the art of making the people believe that they are in power."
msgstr ""
"La política es el arte de hacer creer a la gente que están en el poder."

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:6586
msgid ""
"<span color='green'>Damage increased by 32%</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>Max HP increased by 4 HP.</span>"
