"I submit that the backbone of the cow has been transplanted unscratched into "
"those gloves, where it has proved pitifully inadequate."
msgstr ""
"Sostengo que la espina dorsal de la vaca ha sido trasplantada sin rasguños "
"en esos guantes, donde ha probado ser lamentablemente inadecuada."

