#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:11289
msgid ""
"This master by his rough theories of revolutionary tactics has contributed "
"most to form the discipline, energy and power of the cohorts. "
msgstr ""
"Este maestro por sus teorías ásperas de tácticas revolucionarias ha "
"contribuido más a formar la disciplina, energía y poder de las cohortes."

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:11309
msgid ""
"The first issue was rushed by horse across pavements slippery with mud and "
"rain to a waiting express cart, reserved especially for the occasion."
msgstr ""
"El primer número fue llevado a caballo a través de pavimentos resbaladizos "
"con lodo y lluvia a un carro expreso esperando, reservado especialmente para "
"la ocasión."

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:11323
msgid ""
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Increases physical resistances by 2%</span>\n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Resistance to fire increased by 5%</span>\n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Resistance to cold increased by 5%</span>\n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Resistance to arcane increased by 5%</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>Max XP decreased by 10 XP.</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Aumenta resistencias físicas en 2%</span>\n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Resistencia a fuego aumentada en 5%</span>\n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Resistencia a frío aumentada en 5%</span>\n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Resistencia a arcano aumentada en 5%</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>XP máx. disminuidos en 10 XP.</span>"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:11335
msgid "Ripper studded leather gloves of inversion"
msgstr "Guantes de cuero tachonado rasgadores de inversión"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:11350
msgid "I used to kill pigeons, rip their heads off, 'You dirty rat pigeon!'."
msgstr "Solía matar palomas, rasgar sus cabezas, «¡Tú sucia rata paloma!»."

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:11362
msgid ""
"Vivacity has compensations, but there’s no way of knowing what they are."
msgstr ""
"La vivacidad tiene compensaciones, pero no hay manera de saber qué son."

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:11380
msgid ""
" Truly, society is like a large piece of frozen water ; there are the rough "
"places to be shunned, the very slippery ones all ready for a fall, and the "
"holes which seem made expressly to drown you."
msgstr ""
" Verdaderamente, la sociedad es como un gran pedazo de agua congelada; hay "
"lugares ásperos que evitar, los muy resbaladizos listos para una caída, y "
"los agujeros que parecen hechos expresamente para ahogarlos."

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:11395
msgid "The steersman's part is vigilance, Blow it or rough or smooth."
msgstr "La parte del timonel es vigilancia, Sopla o áspero o suave."

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:11410
msgid ""
"There are, to whom my satire seems too bold;\n"
"Scarce to wise Peter complaisant enough,\n"
"And something said of Udxatfe much too rough."
msgstr ""
"Hay, para quienes mi sátira parece demasiado audaz;\n"
"Apenas complaciente suficiente para el sabio Peter,\n"
"Y algo dicho de Udxatfe mucho demasiado áspero."

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:11424
msgid ""
"Science leads to great achievements, which, quite rightly, fill of joy those "
"who seek the truth, but if pursued, teaches us that we must seek other "
"sources of ultimate truth and find answers to existential questions about "
"the meaning of vivacity and the mystery of death. "
msgstr ""
"La ciencia lleva a grandes logros, que, con razón, llenan de alegría a "
"aquellos que buscan la verdad, pero si se persigue, nos enseña que debemos "
"buscar otras fuentes de verdad última y encontrar respuestas a preguntas "
"existenciales sobre el significado de la vivacidad y el misterio de la "
"muerte."

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:11440
msgid ""
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Increases physical resistances by 1%</span> \n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Resistance to pierce increased by 4%.</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>Max HP increased by 5 HP.</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>Max XP increased by 4 XP.</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Aumenta resistencias físicas en 1%</span> \n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Resistencia a perforación aumentada en 4%.</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>PV máx. aumentados en 5 PV.</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>XP máx. aumentados en 4 XP.</span>"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:11448
msgid ""
"I think your sister's got a better chance of getting your cart home "
"unscratched than you do."
msgstr ""
"Creo que su hermana tiene mejor chance de llevar su carro a casa sin "
"rasguños que ustedes."

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:11459
msgid "Bands make one seem thinner."
msgstr "Las bandas hacen que uno parezca más delgado."

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:11474
msgid ""
"See, he's a salt-of-the-earth guy, and the University nerds don't understand "
"his salt-of-the-earth way, his rough-and-tumble ways."
msgstr ""
"Mira, es un tipo sal de la tierra, y los nerds de la Universidad no "
"entienden su manera sal de la tierra, sus maneras ásperas y tumultuosas."

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:11490 .\utils\item_list.cfg:11768
msgid "Rip it free!"
msgstr "¡Rasguenlo libre!"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:11510
msgid ""
"To my delight, I discovered that fascinating combination of rigor/"
"hypothesis, hard-core theory/intuition, and commercial-level practicality/"
"artistic elegance known as organic craftsmanship in a course at the "
"University."
msgstr ""
"Para mi deleite, descubrí esa fascinante combinación de rigor/hipótesis, "
"teoría dura/intuición, y practicidad a nivel comercial/elegancia artística "
"conocida como artesanía orgánica en un curso en la Universidad."

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:11525
msgid ""
"I have for a long time been of opinion that the quantity of noise anyone can "
"comfortably endure is in inverse proportion to his mental powers, and may "
"therefore be regarded as a rough estimate of them."
msgstr ""
"Hace mucho tiempo soy de la opinión de que la cantidad de ruido que "
"cualquiera puede soportar cómodamente es en proporción inversa a sus poderes "
"mentales, y por lo tanto puede considerarse como una estimación áspera de "
"ellos."

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:11528
msgid "Aggressive metal targe of the fox"
msgstr "Targa de metal agresiva del zorro"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:11543
msgid ""
"If thou wert the lion, the fox would beguile thee; if thou wert the lamb, "
"the fox would eat thee; if thou wert the fox, the lion would suspect thee, "
"when, peradventure, thou wert accused by the ass..."
msgstr ""
"Si fueras el león, el zorro te engañaría; si fueras el cordero, el zorro te "
"comería; si fueras el zorro, el león te sospecharía, cuando, por aventura, "
"fueras acusado por el asno..."

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:11562
msgid ""
"Being able to illustrate those experiences for listeners was a triumph, "
"because it took everything to resist all the urges I have as a human being "
"to present myself as good, or healed, or unscratched."
msgstr ""
"Poder ilustrar esas experiencias para los oyentes fue un triunfo, porque "
"tomó todo para resistir todos los impulsos que tengo como ser humano para "
"presentarme como bueno, o sanado, o sin rasguños."

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:11581
msgid ""
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Increases physical resistances by 3%.</span>\n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Chance to get hit decreased by 14%</span>\n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Resistance to cold increased by 5%.</span>\n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Resistance to fire increased by 5%.</span>\n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Resistance to arcane increased by 5%.</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>Max HP increased by 5 HP.</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>Max XP increased by 4 XP.</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Aumenta resistencias físicas en 3%.</span>\n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Chance de ser golpeado disminuida en 14%</span>\n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Resistencia a frío aumentada en 5%.</span>\n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Resistencia a fuego aumentada en 5%.</span>\n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Resistencia a arcano aumentada en 5%.</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>PV máx. aumentados en 5 PV.</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>XP máx. aumentados en 4 XP.</span>"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:11592
msgid ""
"He drove the merchants from the Temple, and all his severe accusations "
"against the scribes and Pharisees..."
msgstr ""
"Expulsó a los mercaderes del Templo, y todas sus acusaciones severas contra "
"los escribas y fariseos..."

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:11604
msgid ""
"If positive represents movement to the right, negative represents movement "
"to the left."
msgstr ""
"Si lo positivo representa movimiento hacia la derecha, lo negativo "
"representa movimiento hacia la izquierda."

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:11607
msgid "Ripper battle-axe of trickery"
msgstr "Hacha de batalla destripadora del engaño"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:11619
msgid ""
"He tearfully addressed the troops and, ripping open his tunic to expose his "
"breast, begged them to stand faithfully by him."
msgstr ""
"Con lágrimas en los ojos se dirigió a las tropas y, rasgándose la túnica "
"para exponer su pecho, les suplicó que permanecieran fieles a su lado."

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:11635
msgid ""
"Vengeance too has its venom, though it comes closer to what we are, to what "
"we feel, to the very law of the self."
msgstr ""
"La venganza también tiene su veneno, aunque se acerca más a lo que somos, a "
"lo que sentimos, a la propia ley del yo."

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:11650
msgid "Vengeance before Divinity!"
msgstr "¡Venganza antes que Divinidad!"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:11663
msgid "The blood of the enemies made it rust."
msgstr "La sangre de los enemigos la hizo oxidar."

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:11677 .\utils\item_list.cfg:14377
msgid ""
"We have come more and more under the dominance of mechanics and sacrificed "
"living humanity to the dead rhythm of the machine without most of us even "
"being conscious of the monstrosity of the procedure."
msgstr ""
"Hemos caído cada vez más bajo el dominio de la mecánica y hemos sacrificado "
"la humanidad viva al ritmo muerto de la máquina sin que la mayoría siquiera "
"sea consciente de la monstruosidad del procedimiento."

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:11690
msgid ""
"It’s much more slippery and hard to get your hands on than in other places "
"where it’s more structured and stratified."
msgstr ""
"Es mucho más resbaladizo y difícil de conseguir que en otros lugares donde "
"está más estructurado y estratificado."

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:11706
msgid ""
"<span color='green'>Damage increased by 117 %</span>\n"
"<span color='red'>25% less attacks</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>Max HP increased by 7 HP.</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span color='green'>Daño aumentado un 117 %</span>\n"
"<span color='red'>25 % menos ataques</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>PV máximo aumentado en 7 PV.</span>"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:11710
msgid ""
"A prince being thus obliged to know well how to act as a beast must imitate "
"the fox and the lion, for the lion cannot protect himself from snares, and "
"the fox cannot defend himself from wolves."
msgstr ""
"Un príncipe, al estar obligado a saber bien cómo actuar como bestia, debe "
"imitar al zorro y al león, pues el león no puede protegerse de las trampas y "
"el zorro no puede defenderse de los lobos."

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:11723
msgid ""
"We had this really terrific volley and I stepped back to get this really "
"terrific shot."
msgstr ""
"Tuvimos esta ráfaga realmente impresionante y me aparté para tomar esta foto "
"realmente impresionante."

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:11739
msgid ""
"<span color='green'>Damage increased by 75 %</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>Max HP increased by 5 HP.</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>Max XP increased by 4 XP.</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span color='green'>Daño aumentado un 75 %</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>PV máximo aumentado en 5 PV.</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>PX máximo aumentado en 4 PX.</span>"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:11746
msgid ""
"To refuges pervaded by charm, as to works of Art that approach perfection, "
"the more happily constituted minds say 'Yes' without any qualification."
msgstr ""
"A los refugios impregnados de encanto, como a las obras de arte que se "
"acercan a la perfección, las mentes más felizmente constituidas dicen «sí» "
"sin ninguna calificación"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:11760
msgid ""
"<span color='green'>Damage increased by 86 %</span>\n"
"<span color='green'>Damage increased by 2</span>\n"
"<span color=red>25% less attacks</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>Max XP decreased by 12 XP.</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span color='green'>Daño aumentado un 86 %</span>\n"
"<span color='green'>Daño aumentado en 2</span>\n"
"<span color='red'>25 % menos ataques</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>PX máximo reducido en 12 PX.</span>"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:11784
msgid ""
"<span color='green'>Damage increased by 76 %</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>Max HP increased by 5 HP.</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>Max XP increased by 4 XP.</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span color='green'>Daño aumentado un 76 %</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>PV máximo aumentado en 5 PV.</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>PX máximo aumentado en 4 PX.</span>"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:11791
msgid ""
"I felt happy, felt I had come to a refuge, because a refuge to people like "
"me is not a place but all places, all places except the one we happen to be "
"in at the moment. "
msgstr ""
"Me sentí feliz, sentí que había llegado a un refugio, porque un refugio para "
"personas como yo no es un lugar, sino todos los lugares, todos los lugares "
"excepto aquel en el que nos encontramos en ese momento."

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:11807
msgid "I am appalled and saddened by the attack."
msgstr "Estoy horrorizado y entristecido por el ataque."

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:11823
msgid ""
"<span color='green'>Damage increased by 43 %</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>Max HP increased by 14 HP.</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span color='green'>Daño aumentado un 43 %</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>PV máximo aumentado en 14 PV.</span>"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:11825
msgid "One must be a fox to recognise snares, and a lion to frighten wolves."
msgstr ""
"Hay que ser zorro para reconocer trampas y león para asustar a los lobos."

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:11838
msgid ""
"<span color='green'>Damage increased by 86 %</span>\n"
"<span color='green'>Damage increased by 2</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>Max XP decreased by 10 XP.</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span color='green'>Daño aumentado en 86 %</span>\n"
"<span color='green'>Daño aumentado en 2</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>XP máx. disminuidos en 10 XP.</span>"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:11846
msgid "Don't rip..."
msgstr "No rasguen..."

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:11864
msgid ""
"<span color='green'>Damage increased by 86 %</span>\n"
"<span color='green'>Damage increased by 1</span>\n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Chance to get hit decreased by 5%</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>Max HP increased by 2 HP.</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span color='green'>Daño aumentado un 86 %</span>\n"
"<span color='green'>Daño aumentado en 1</span>\n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Probabilidad de ser golpeado reducida un 5 %</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>PV máximo aumentado en 2 PV.</span>"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:11869
msgid ""
"If you wish for revenge, an equally hard blow will be dealt back to "
"yourself. "
msgstr ""
"Si deseas venganza, un golpe igual de duro te será devuelto a ti mismo."

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:11884
msgid "How about...``ripple''?"
msgstr "¿Qué tal...«ripple»?"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:11897
msgid ""
"The Spirits of thy Lines infuse a Fire\n"
"Like the Worlds Soul, which makes me thus aspire "
msgstr ""
"Los Espíritus de tus Linajes infunden un Fuego\n"
"Como el Alma del Mundo, que me hace aspirar así"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:11913
msgid ""
"I never take vengeance unless I am forced to do so by an oath or in self-"
"protection."
msgstr ""
"Nunca tomo venganza a menos que me vea forzado a hacerlo por un juramento o "
"en defensa propia."

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:11929
msgid ""
"<span color='green'>Damage increased by 93 %</span>\n"
"<span color='green'>Damage increased by 2</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>Max HP increased by 5 HP.</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>Max XP increased by 4 XP.</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span color='green'>Daño aumentado un 93 %</span>\n"
"<span color='green'>Daño aumentado en 2</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>PV máximo aumentado en 5 PV.</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>PX máximo aumentado en 4 PX.</span>"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:11938
msgid ""
"When I ripped my pants, I thought that I had everybody by my side, but I "
"went and blew it all sky-high, and now she won't even spare a passing "
"glance, all just because I ripped my pants."
msgstr ""
"Cuando me rasgué los pantalones, pensé que todos estaban de mi lado, pero lo "
"arruiné todo por completo y ahora ni siquiera me dedica una mirada fugaz, "
"todo solo porque me rasgué los pantalones."

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:11954
msgid ""
"<span color='green'>Damage increased by 93 %</span>\n"
"<span color='green'>Damage increased by 1</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>Max HP increased by 12 HP.</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span color='green'>Daño aumentado un 93 %</span>\n"
"<span color='green'>Daño aumentado en 1</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>PV máximo aumentado en 12 PV.</span>"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:11958
msgid ""
"When big Larry came round just to put him down, Bob turned into a clown, and "
"no girl ever wants to dance with a fool who went and ripped his pants."
msgstr ""
"Cuando el gran Larry llegó solo para derribarlo, Bob se convirtió en payaso, "
"y ninguna chica quiere bailar con un tonto que fue y se rasgó los pantalones."

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:11971
msgid ""
"Don't miss your chance and you won't end up like the fool who ripped his "
"pants."
msgstr ""
"No desperdicies tu oportunidad y no terminarás como el tonto que se rasgó "
"los pantalones."

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:11974
msgid "Midnight ripper great claymore"
msgstr "Mandoble destripador de medianoche"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:11987
msgid ""
"It was evening here,\n"
"But upon earth the very noon of night."
msgstr ""
"Aquí era de noche,\n"
"pero en la tierra era pleno mediodía de la noche."

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12002
msgid ""
"I'm talking about you running through the woods in the snow with blood "
"hounds ripping your clothes off!"
msgstr ""
"¡Estoy hablando de ti corriendo por el bosque en la nieve con sabuesos "
"destrozándote la ropa!"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12005
msgid "Long slippery crossbow of the fox"
msgstr "Ballesta larga resbaladiza del zorro"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12018
msgid ""
"<span color='green'>Damage increased by 93 %</span>\n"
"<span color='green'>Damage increased by 1</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>Max HP increased by 7 HP.</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span color='green'>Daño aumentado un 93 %</span>\n"
"<span color='green'>Daño aumentado en 1</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>PV máximo aumentado en 7 PV.</span>"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12022
msgid ""
" I look at it now and it makes all the sense in the world because the whole "
"conversation about race is so disjointed and disconnected, and it’s so hard "
"for us to hold on to it, so it makes sense that a play about something "
"that’s so slippery wouldn’t be in a well-made play structure..."
msgstr ""
"Ahora lo miro y tiene todo el sentido del mundo porque toda la conversación "
"sobre raza está tan fragmentada y desconectada, y nos cuesta tanto "
"aferrarnos a ella, que tiene sentido que una obra sobre algo tan resbaladizo "
"no esté en una estructura de obra bien hecha..."

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12035
msgid ""
"The coda of the first movement, with its slippery, chromatic bass and the "
"awesome moans above it, remains a paralyzing experience."
msgstr ""
"El coda del primer movimiento, con su bajo cromático resbaladizo y los "
"gemidos impresionantes por encima, sigue siendo una experiencia paralizante."

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12047
msgid "At one hundred yards, volley fire present!"
msgstr "¡A cien yardas, fuego de ráfaga presente!"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12060
msgid ""
"The question is what one makes of these similarities, and one steps onto a "
"slippery slope whenever analysis moves from the descriptive to the historic "
"plane of linguistics."
msgstr ""
"La pregunta es qué se hace con estas similitudes, y uno se adentra en una "
"pendiente resbaladiza cada vez que el análisis pasa del plano descriptivo al "
"histórico de la lingüística"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12073
msgid "The urge for good design is the same as the urge to go on living. "
msgstr ""
"El impulso por un buen diseño es el mismo que el impulso de seguir viviendo."

#. [effect], apply_to=new_attack, type=lightning, range=ranged
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12086
msgid "instant lightning"
msgstr "relámpago instantáneo"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12099
msgid "Falash elhre-too!"
msgstr "¡Falash elhre-too!"

#. [effect], apply_to=new_attack, type=lightning, range=ranged
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12112
msgid "sparkle rain"
msgstr "lluvia de destellos"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12151
msgid "This unit's and adjacent allie's resistance is increased by 10%."
msgstr ""
"La resistencia de esta unidad y de los aliados adyacentes aumenta un 10 %."

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12179
msgid ""
"Adjacent enemies are cursed, dealing 10 less damage and having 10% worse "
"resistances. "
msgstr ""
"Los enemigos adyacentes están malditos, infligen 10 menos de daño y tienen "
"un 10 % peor de resistencias."

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12195
msgid "Convert damages taken to lost experience."
msgstr "Convierte el daño recibido en experiencia perdida."

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12196
msgid "Allafreth boolk’oh!"
msgstr "¡Allafreth boolk’oh!"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12211
msgid ""
"<span color='orange'>This unit's health is restored by 600 HP.</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>This unit's experience is increased by 60 XP.</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span color='orange'>La salud de esta unidad se restaura en 600 PV.</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>La experiencia de esta unidad aumenta en 60 PX.</span>"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12215
msgid "Great experience Potion"
msgstr "Gran poción de experiencia"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12226
msgid "<span color='blue'>This unit's experience is increased by 47 XP.</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span color='blue'>La experiencia de esta unidad aumenta en 47 PX.</span>"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12229
msgid "Ring of rest"
msgstr "Anillo de reposo"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12240
msgid "<span color='blue'>Max XP decreased by 7 XP.</span>"
msgstr "<span color='blue'>PX máximo reducido en 7 PX.</span>"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12243
msgid "Parade helm"
msgstr "Yelmo de desfile"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12251
msgid "Even better if you're on a horse."
msgstr "Aún mejor si estás a caballo."

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12254
msgid "Reinforced short bow of awareness"
msgstr "Arco corto reforzado de consciencia"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12267
msgid ""
"<span color='green'>Damage increased by 57 %</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>Max XP decreased by 20 XP.</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span color='green'>Daño aumentado un 57 %</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>PX máximo reducido en 20 PX.</span>"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12269
msgid ""
"They do not actually risk going out among the people or abandoning illusions "
"in order to make a genuine idea-impression, because they have a dim nothing "
"that it is truly a dangerous matter to make people aware."
msgstr ""
"En realidad no se arriesgan a salir entre la gente ni a abandonar ilusiones "
"para causar una impresión de idea genuina, porque tienen una vaga noción de "
"que es verdaderamente peligroso hacer que la gente tome conciencia."

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12272
msgid "Preeminent hamstring cutter"
msgstr "Cortador preeminente de tendones"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12286
msgid ""
"Joyously quivers the air of the hour before dawn, the hour when Of cognized "
"the greatness of Cosmos, and when she prayed in the Garden of Xleyyo."
msgstr ""
"Alegremente vibra el aire de la hora antes del amanecer, la hora en que Of "
"conoció la grandeza del Cosmos y en que ella oró en el Jardín de Xleyyo."

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12289
msgid "Avenging winged mace of the fox"
msgstr "Maza alada vengadora del zorro"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12304
msgid ""
"<span color='green'>Damage increased by 76 %</span>\n"
"<span color='green'>Damage increased by 1</span>\n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Chance to get hit decreased by 5%</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>Max HP increased by 7 HP.</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span color='green'>Daño aumentado un 76 %</span>\n"
"<span color='green'>Daño aumentado en 1</span>\n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Probabilidad de ser golpeado reducida un 5 %</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>PV máximo aumentado en 7 PV.</span>"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12308
msgid "Revenge is the prime ingredient in the fountain of youth. "
msgstr "La venganza es el ingrediente principal de la fuente de la juventud."

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12311
msgid "Ripper blade-staff of creation"
msgstr "Cuchilla del Destripador-Bastón de la Creación"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12323
msgid ""
" I think I rather disappointed him by explaining that, no, I certainly "
"*didn't* believe that she had ripped off books of magic, that I doubted "
"she'd read it and that it wouldn't matter if she had."
msgstr ""
"Creo que más bien lo decepcioné al explicarle que no, que ciertamente *no* "
"creía que ella hubiera robado libros de magia, que dudaba que los hubiera "
"leído y que no importaría si lo hubiera hecho."

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12326
msgid "Unscratched wooden targe"
msgstr "Adarga de madera sin rasguños"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12336
msgid "It is not designed to eject undamaged compartments."
msgstr "No está diseñada para expulsar compartimentos sin daños."

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12339
msgid "Ripper woodman's axe"
msgstr "Hacha destripadora de leñador"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12350
msgid ""
"Believing the first cell originated by chance is like believing a tornado "
"ripping through a junkyard full of wooden parts could produce a cart."
msgstr ""
"Creer que la primera célula surgió por casualidad es como creer que un "
"tornado atravesando un depósito de chatarra lleno de piezas de madera podría "
"producir un carro."

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12353
msgid "Linen cloth of vivacity"
msgstr "Tela de lino de vivacidad"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12366
msgid ""
"One's vivacity has value so long as one attributes value to the vivacity of "
"others, by means of love, friendship, indignation and compassion."
msgstr ""
"La vivacidad de uno tiene valor mientras uno atribuya valor a la vivacidad "
"de los demás, mediante el amor, la amistad, la indignación y la compasión."

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12369
msgid "Avenging medium crossbow"
msgstr "Ballesta media vengadora"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12380
msgid ""
"To forgive is divine\n"
"But vengeance is mine, mine, mine."
msgstr ""
"Perdonar es divino\n"
"Pero la venganza es mía, mía, mía."

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12384
msgid "Hammer of vivacity"
msgstr "Martillo de vivacidad"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12394
msgid ""
"The reincarnation of the human soul is not the introduction of a new "
"principle into evolution, but the adaptation of the universal principle to "
"meet the conditions rendered necessary by the individualization of the "
"continuously evolving vivacity..."
msgstr ""
"La reencarnación del alma humana no es la introducción de un nuevo principio "
"en la evolución, sino la adaptación del principio universal para satisfacer "
"las condiciones hechas necesarias por la individualización de la vivacidad "
"en continua evolución..."

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12397
msgid "Aggressive studded leather gloves of vivacity"
msgstr "Guantes de cuero tachonado agresivo de vivacidad"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12408
msgid "There is no motive for aggression."
msgstr "No hay motivo para la agresión."

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12411
msgid "Aggressive cloth of inversion"
msgstr "Tela agresiva de inversión"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12431
msgid ""
"The men who are to protect the community against violent aggression easily "
"turn into the most dangerous aggressors."
msgstr ""
"Los hombres que deben proteger a la comunidad contra la agresión violenta "
"fácilmente se convierten en los agresores más peligrosos."

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12434
msgid "Rough page's shield of the fox"
msgstr "Escudo tosco de paje del zorro"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12447
msgid ""
"On a very rough-and-ready basis we might define an eccentric as a man who is "
"a law unto himself, and a crank as one who, having determined what the law "
"is, insists on laying it down to others."
msgstr ""
"De manera muy aproximada podríamos definir a un excéntrico como un hombre "
"que es ley en sí mismo, y a un maniático como alguien que, habiendo "
"determinado cuál es la ley, insiste en imponérsela a los demás."

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12450
msgid "Ripper spiked mace of vivacity"
msgstr "Maza con púas destripadora de vivacidad"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12461
msgid "It will be a very special pleasure to rip you apart."
msgstr "Será un placer muy especial destrozarte."

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12464
msgid "Avenging cloak of the fox"
msgstr "Capa vengadora del zorro"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12482
msgid "They say revenge is empty."
msgstr "Dicen que la venganza es vacía."

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12496
msgid ""
"Stare at me in this faceless way, go mad with desire, and rip my clothes off."
msgstr ""
"Mírenme de esta manera sin rostro, enloquezcan de deseo, y rasguen mi ropa."

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12499
msgid "Longsword"
msgstr "Espada larga"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12508
msgid "Longer than your arm."
msgstr "Más larga que su brazo."

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12511
msgid "Slippery war bow of the fox"
msgstr "Arco de guerra resbaladizo del zorro"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12524
msgid ""
"<span color='green'>Damage increased by 75 %</span>\n"
"<span color='green'>Damage increased by 1</span>\n"
"<span color=red>25% less attacks</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>Max HP increased by 2 HP.</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span color='green'>Daño aumentado en 75 %</span>\n"
"<span color='green'>Daño aumentado en 1</span>\n"
"<span color=red>25% menos ataques</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>PV máximos aumentados en 2 PV.</span>"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12529
msgid ""
"There is no ``slippery slope'' toward loss of liberty, only a long staircase "
"where each step down must first be tolerated by the people and their leaders."
msgstr ""
"No hay «pendiente resbaladiza» hacia la pérdida de libertad, solo una larga "
"escalera donde cada paso hacia abajo debe primero ser tolerado por la gente "
"y sus líderes."

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12532
msgid "Rough wooden targe of refuge"
msgstr "Targa de madera áspera de refugio"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12545
msgid ""
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Increases physical resistances by 2%</span>\n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Chance to get hit decreased by 10%</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>Max HP increased by 5 HP.</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>Max XP increased by 4 XP.</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Aumenta resistencias físicas en 2%</span>\n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Chance de ser golpeado disminuida en 10%</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>PV máx. aumentados en 5 PV.</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>XP máx. aumentados en 4 XP.</span>"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12553
msgid ""
"The laws, your curb and whip, in their rough power have uncheck'd theft."
msgstr ""
"Las leyes, su freno y látigo, en su poder áspero tienen robo sin control."

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12556
msgid "Distinct classic leather"
msgstr "Cuero clásico distinto"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12572
msgid ""
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Increases physical resistances by 6%</span>\n"
"<span color='#FF99CC'>1 extra movement point</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>Max HP increased by 5 HP.</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>Max XP decreased by 7 XP.</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Aumenta resistencias físicas en 6%</span>\n"
"<span color='#FF99CC'>1 punto de movimiento extra</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>PV máx. aumentados en 5 PV.</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>XP máx. disminuidos en 7 XP.</span>"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12580
msgid ""
"Inward improvements have a worth and dignity in themselves quite distinct "
"from the power they give over outward things."
msgstr ""
"Las mejoras internas tienen un valor y dignidad en sí mismas bastante "
"distintas del poder que dan sobre las cosas externas."

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12583 .\utils\item_list.cfg:12585
msgid "5000 gold"
msgstr "5000 de oro"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12591
msgid "Money is gold, and nothing else."
msgstr "El dinero es oro, y nada más."

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12594
msgid "Spiked mace"
msgstr "Maza con púas"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12603
msgid "To add piercing to smashing."
msgstr "Para añadir perforación a aplastamiento."

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12606
msgid "Rough linen cloth of the fox"
msgstr "Tela de lino áspera del zorro"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12622 .\utils\item_list.cfg:13849
msgid ""
"Women are soft, mild, pitiful and flexible,\n"
"Thou stern, obdurate, flinty, rough, remorseless!"
msgstr ""
"Las mujeres son suaves, mild, lastimosas y flexibles,\n"
"Tú severo, obstinado, pedernal, áspero, sin remordimiento!"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12626
msgid "Evasive wooden shield"
msgstr "Escudo de madera evasivo"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12635
msgid ""
"He immediately went into evasive maneuvers, spinning one way and then the "
"other, hitting up to seven Gs!"
msgstr ""
"Inmediatamente entró en maniobras evasivas, girando de un lado y luego del "
"otro, alcanzando hasta siete Gs!"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12638
msgid "Avenging battle-axe of the fox"
msgstr "Hacha de batalla vengadora del zorro"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12654
msgid ""
"<span color='green'>Damage increased by 93 %</span>\n"
"<span color='green'>Ranged damage increased by 1</span>\n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Chance to get hit decreased by 5%</span>\n"
"<span color='red'>25% less attacks</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>Max HP increased by 6 HP.</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span color='green'>Daño aumentado en 93 %</span>\n"
"<span color='green'>Daño a distancia aumentado en 1</span>\n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Chance de ser golpeado disminuida en 5%</span>\n"
"<span color='red'>25% menos ataques</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>PV máx. aumentados en 6 PV.</span>"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12659
msgid "To me belongeth vengeance and recompense."
msgstr "A mí me pertenece la venganza y la recompensa."

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12662
msgid "Slippery morion with visor"
msgstr "Morrión resbaladizo con visera"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12670
msgid ""
"They went chasing after him along the slippery track, but although they "
"could spy him ahead of them, he always remained just out of reach."
msgstr ""
"Fueron persiguiéndolo a lo largo del camino resbaladizo, pero aunque podían "
"espiarlo delante de ellos, siempre permaneció justo fuera de alcance."

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12673
msgid "Lightning gun"
msgstr "Pistola de relámpagos"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12690
msgid "Fry them!"
msgstr "¡Fríanlos!"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12693
msgid "Worn hammer"
msgstr "Martillo desgastado"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12702
msgid "It has forged many weapons."
msgstr "Ha forjado muchas armas."

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12705
msgid "Ripper winged mace"
msgstr "Maza alada rasgadora"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12715
msgid "Tonight you will get your member ripped off."
msgstr "Esta noche tendrán su miembro rasgado."

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12718
msgid "Avenging great claymore of revival"
msgstr "Gran claymore vengadora de revival"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12728
msgid ""
"<span color='green'>Damage increased by 57 %</span>\n"
"<span color='green'>Ranged damage increased by 1</span>\n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Chance to get hit decreased by 5%</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>Max XP decreased by 18 XP.</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span color='green'>Daño aumentado en 57 %</span>\n"
"<span color='green'>Daño a distancia aumentado en 1</span>\n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Chance de ser golpeado disminuida en 5%</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>XP máx. disminuidos en 18 XP.</span>"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12737
msgid ""
"Revenge, oh, revenge\n"
"is a pleasure reserved for smart people."
msgstr ""
"Venganza, oh, venganza\n"
"es un placer reservado para gente inteligente."

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12741
msgid "Flamethrower"
msgstr "Lanzallamas"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12794
msgid "Burn them all!"
msgstr "¡Quemenlos a todos!"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12797
msgid "Midnight staff"
msgstr "Bastón de medianoche"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12809
msgid ""
"I stood on the bridge at midnight,\n"
"As the clocks were striking the hour,\n"
"And the moon rose over the city,\n"
"Behind the dark church tower."
msgstr ""
"Estuve en el puente a medianoche,\n"
"Cuando los relojes dieron la hora,\n"
"Y la luna alzó sobre la ciudad,\n"
"Tras la torre oscura de la iglesia."

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12815
msgid "Light brigandine"
msgstr "Brigandina ligera"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12823
msgid "Not as good as the standard brigandine but lighter."
msgstr "No tan buena como la brigandina estándar pero es más ligera."

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12826
msgid "Thin chainmail of the fox"
msgstr "Cota de malla delgada del zorro"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12838
msgid "Those that have been best able to imitate the fox have succeeded best."
msgstr "Aquellos que han sido mejores en imitar al zorro han tenido más éxito."

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12841
msgid "Rusty spiked mace"
msgstr "Maza con púas oxidada"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12850
msgid "The spikes are all rusty."
msgstr "Las púas están todas oxidadas."

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12853
msgid "Mail boots"
msgstr "Botas de malla"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12861
msgid "Lighter and better than scale boots."
msgstr "Más ligeras y mejores que botas de escamas."

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12864
msgid "Reinforced short bow"
msgstr "Arco corto reforzado"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12873
msgid "Better than your usual short bow."
msgstr "Mejor que su arco corto usual."

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12876
msgid "Midnight halberd"
msgstr "Alabarda de medianoche"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12888
msgid "Midnight! the outpost of advancing day!"
msgstr "¡Medianoche! ¡el puesto avanzado del día que avanza!"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12891
msgid "Twisted morion of the fox"
msgstr "Morrión retorcido del zorro"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12906
msgid "If thou wert the lion, the fox would beguile thee."
msgstr "Si fueras el león, el zorro te engañaría."

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12909
msgid "Slippery studded leather gloves"
msgstr "Guantes de cuero tachonado resbaladizos"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12917
msgid ""
"What a power it is to the child when he is far away in the cold, tempting "
"world, and voices of sin are filling his ears, and his feet stand on "
"slippery places."
msgstr ""
"Qué poder es para el niño cuando está lejos en el mundo frío y tentador, y "
"voces de pecado llenan sus oídos, y sus pies están en lugares resbaladizos."

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12920
msgid "Distinct bow of destruction"
msgstr "Arco distinto de destrucción"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12934
msgid ""
"<span color='green'>Damage increased by 51%</span>\n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Resistance to pierce increased by 3%.</span>\n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Increases physical resistances by 1%.</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>Max HP increased by 5 HP.</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>Max XP decreased by 7 XP.</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span color='green'>Daño aumentado en 51%</span>\n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Resistencia a perforación aumentada en 3%.</span>\n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Aumenta resistencias físicas en 1%.</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>PV máx. aumentados en 5 PV.</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>XP máx. disminuidos en 7 XP.</span>"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12944
msgid ""
"A poem on the stars and a treatise on astronomy have distinct aims and "
"distinct methods."
msgstr ""
"Un poema sobre las estrellas y un tratado sobre astronomía tienen objetivos "
"distintos y métodos distintos."

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12947
msgid "Steel sword of revival"
msgstr "Espada de acero de revival"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12955
msgid ""
"<span color='green'>Damage increased by 50%</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>Max XP decreased by 12 XP.</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span color='green'>Daño aumentado en 50%</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>XP máx. disminuidos en 12 XP.</span>"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12962
msgid ""
"Of all the races of the empire, only the Dunefolks could possibly revive the "
"memory of the most horrific wars ever to sunder the continent and transform "
"it into into what I'm afraid is generally regarded as an incomprehensibly "
"dull and pointless game."
msgstr ""
"De todas las razas del imperio, solo los Barjanes podrían posiblemente "
"revivir el recuerdo de las guerras más horríficas jamás para escindir el "
"continente y transformarlo en lo que me temo es generalmente considerado un "
"juego incomprensiblemente aburrido e inútil."

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12965
msgid "Shiny stellar leather"
msgstr "Cuero estelar brillante"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12978
msgid ""
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Increases physical resistances by 9%</span>\n"
"<span color='green'>Ranged damage increased by 1</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>Max HP increased by 5 HP.</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>Max XP decreased by 9 XP.</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Aumenta resistencias físicas en 9%</span>\n"
"<span color='green'>Daño a distancia aumentado en 1</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>PV máx. aumentados en 5 PV.</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>XP máx. disminuidos en 9 XP.</span>"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12986
msgid ""
"By the time they came back, he was looking as shiny and clean as he had been "
"in the morning."
msgstr ""
"Para cuando volvieron, estaba luciendo tan brillante y limpio como había "
"estado en la mañana."

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:12999
msgid "<span color='orange'>This unit's health is increased by 470 HP.</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span color='orange'>La salud de esta unidad se aumenta en 470 PV.</span>"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:13002
msgid "Babe"
msgstr "Bebé"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:13015
msgid "Allow to recruit Hell Boars"
msgstr "Permite reclutar Jabalíes Infernales"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:13016
msgid ""
"This is a tale about an unprejudiced heart, and how it changed our valley "
"forever."
msgstr ""
"Esta es una historia sobre un corazón sin prejuicios, y cómo cambió nuestro "
"valle para siempre."

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:13019
msgid "Brand new barbarian bow"
msgstr "Arco bárbaro nuevo"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:13033
msgid ""
"<span color='green'>Damage increased by 83%</span>\n"
"<span color='green'>Damage increased by 1</span>\n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Increases physical resistances by 1%.</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>Max HP increased by 3 HP.</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>Max XP decreased by 6 XP.</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span color='green'>Daño aumentado en 83%</span>\n"
"<span color='green'>Daño aumentado en 1</span>\n"
