"<span color='green'>Damage increased by 112 %</span>\n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Increases physical resistances by 1%</span>\n"
"<span color='green'>Enemy resistance to pierce decreased by 2%</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span color='green'>Daño aumentado en 112 %</span>\n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Aumenta resistencias físicas en 1%</span>\n"
"<span color='green'>Resistencia enemiga a perforación disminuida en 2%</span>"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:13414
msgid ""
"A life of love is one of continual growth, where the doors and windows of "
"experience are always open to the wonder and magic that life offers."
msgstr ""
"Una vida de amor es una de crecimiento continuo, donde las puertas y "
"ventanas de la experiencia siempre están abiertas a la maravilla y magia que "
"la vida ofrece."

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:13417
msgid "Staff of refuge"
msgstr "Bastón de refugio"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:13429 .\utils\item_list.cfg:13699
