msgstr "Guanteletes de arnés ásperos"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:14865
msgid ""
"On your emblem, which a roaring sea\n"
"Shields with its rough waves,\n"
"Behind the bare summit of a volcano, of a volcano,\n"
"There is a star, there is a star of clear light."
msgstr ""
"En su emblema, que un mar rugiente\n"
"Protege con sus olas ásperas,\n"
"Detrás de la cumbre desnuda de un volcán, de un volcán,\n"
"Hay una estrella, hay una estrella de luz clara."

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:14871
msgid "Great pavise of the fox"
msgstr "Gran pavés del zorro"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:14884
msgid ""
"When the fox hath once got in his nose,\n"
"He'll soon find means to make the body follow."
msgstr ""
"Cuando el zorro una vez ha metido su nariz,\n"
"Pronto encontrará medios para que el cuerpo siga."

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:14888
msgid "Great ripper shocking claymore"
msgstr "Gran claymore chocante rasgadora"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:14899 .\utils\item_list.cfg:15770
msgid ""
"If ripping throats gets that weapon back, I'll rip as many throats as I have "
"to!"
msgstr ""
"¡Si rasgar gargantas recupera esa arma, rasgaré tantas gargantas como tenga "
"que!"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:14902
msgid "Slippery long crossbow of volley"
msgstr "Ballesta larga resbaladiza de ráfaga"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:14912
msgid ""
"If you get influenced by anybody else's negative thoughts, it can be a "
"slippery slope down."
msgstr ""
"Si se influencian por los pensamientos negativos de alguien más, puede ser "
"una pendiente resbaladiza hacia abajo."

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:14915
msgid "Ripper cloth of the fox"
msgstr "Tela rasgadora del zorro"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:14932
msgid ""
"Fascists would pull your eyes out with teaspoons, they'd rip your nails out "
"with tweezers."
msgstr ""
"Los fascistas sacarían sus ojos con cucharitas, rasgarían sus uñas con "
"pinzas."

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:14935
msgid "Distinct chainmail"
msgstr "Cota de malla distintiva"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:14952
msgid ""
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Increases physical resistances by 15%.</span>\n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Resistance to pierce increased by 3%.</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>Max HP increased by 5 HP.</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>Max XP decreased by 7 XP.</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Aumenta las resistencias físicas en un 15%.</span>\n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Resistencia a perforación aumentada en un 3%.</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>PV máximos aumentados en 5 PV.</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>PX máximos disminuidos en 7 PX.</span>"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:14956
msgid ""
"A modern theory of knowledge which takes account of the relational as "
"distinct from the merely relative character of all historical knowledge must "
"start with the assumption that there are spheres of thought in which it is "
"impossible to conceive of absolute truth existing independently of the "
"values and position of the subject and unrelated to the social context."
msgstr ""
"Una teoría moderna del conocimiento que toma en cuenta el carácter "
"relacional como distinto del meramente relativo de todo el conocimiento "
"histórico debe comenzar con la suposición de que hay esferas de pensamiento "
"en las que es imposible concebir la verdad absoluta existiendo "
"independientemente de los valores y la posición del sujeto y sin relación "
"con el contexto social."

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:14959
msgid "Romulus and Remus"
msgstr "Rómulo y Remo"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:14972
