#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:14989
msgid "Rough chainmail of the fox"
msgstr "Cota de malla tosca del zorro"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:15001
msgid ""
"Like a rough orator, that brings more truth\n"
"Than rhetoric, to make good his accusation."
msgstr ""
"Como un orador tosco, que trae más verdad\n"
"Que la retórica, para hacer buena su acusación."

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:15005
msgid "BFG"
msgstr "BFG"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:15018
msgid "Allow to recruit Ogres"
msgstr "Permite reclutar Ogros"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:15019
msgid "That's what I call big."
msgstr "Eso es lo que llamo grande."

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:15022
msgid "Unscratched mail gloves"
msgstr "Guantes de malla sin rayones"

#. [object]
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:15031
msgid ""
"The bee collects honey from flowers in such a way as to do the least damage "
"or destruction to them, and he leaves them whole, undamaged and fresh, just "
"as he found them."
msgstr ""
"La abeja recolecta miel de las flores de tal manera que causa el menor daño "
"o destrucción a ellas, y las deja enteras, sin daños y frescas, justo como "
"las encontró."

